(5, 'Amaterasu', 'The Shining Light', 'Japanese', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/amaterasu.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/amaterasu.jpg', 'Divine Presence', 'Heavenly Reflection', 'Glorious Charge', 'Dazzling Offensive', 'Illuminating Strike', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/divine-presence.jpg', 'Amaterasu harnesses the power of her jewel, healing herself every second for 4 seconds and creating a persistent aura that buffs nearby allied gods. Every time this ability is activated the aura switches between Valor and Benevolence. ', 'Amaterasu charges her mirror for 5 seconds. While the mirror is charging she takes decreased damage. By activating the ability again or at the end of 5 seconds she will fire her mirror straight ahead, dealing damage. The mirror can be charged by successfully attacking enemies or from taking damage, and will deal up to double the base damage when fully charged.', 'Amaterasu shines light off of her sacred blade, silencing all enemies in front of her. She then dashes forward while dealing damage, piercing through minions or stopping at the first god hit.  ', 'Amaterasu focuses the power of the heavens into an impressive 3 strike combination attack. The 2nd hit will do 20% more base damage and slow enemies by 30%. The 3rd hit will do 40% more base damage and stun enemies. She must hit an enemy with the 1st hit to receive the increased damage and CC on the 2nd hit. The same rule applies to the 2nd and 3rd hits.', 'Amaterasu illuminates enemies she hits with basic attacks. After 3 hits on the same target the enemy gains an aura, exposing their weaknesses and causing them to take more damage from all sources. Any other enemies that come near the afflicted target are weakened as well.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/heavenly-reflection.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/glorious-charge.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/dazzling-offensive.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/illuminating-strike.jpg', '9 seconds', '12 seconds', '18 seconds', '95/90/85/80/75 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70  mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '70/75/80/85/90  mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"35\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Debuff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Heal Per Tick:\",\"value\":\"15/25/35/45/55 (+5% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Benevolence Aura:\",\"value\":\"5/9/13/17/21 % Move Speed\"},{\"description\":\"Valor Aura:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30 Bonus Power\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Self Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"3/6/9/12/15%\"},{\"description\":\"Mirror Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/100/130/160/190 (60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Full Charge Damage:\",\"value\":\"140/200/260/320/380\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Silence Duration:\",\"value\":\"1s\"},{\"description\":\"Dash Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/120/180/240/300(60% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Per Strike:\",\"value\":\"80/120/160/200/240 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s\"},{\"description