(7, 'Anubis', 'God of the Dead', 'Egyptian', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/anubis.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/anubis.jpg', 'Plague of Locusts', 'Mummify', 'Grasping Hands', 'Death Gaze', 'Sorrow', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/plague-of-locusts.jpg', 'A plague of locusts bellows forth from Anubis\' mouth, smothering all enemies in the area and doing damage every .5s for 3s. Anubis is immune to knockback while channeling.', 'Anubis fires a bandage projectile, mummifying and stunning his target.', 'Anubis calls for help from the underworld as hands penetrate the ground and claw at his enemies, doing damage and Slowing every .5s for 2s.', 'Anubis focuses all of his energy into a piercing gaze, doing damage to all enemies in the path, every 0.1 seconds for 3 seconds.', 'All of Anubis\' abilities steal Physical and Magical Protection from the target and increase his Healing obtained from Magical Lifesteal. These effects stack on every tick of Anubis\' abilities. Sorrow also grants Anubis an additional 30% reduction to all Crowd Control durations.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mummify.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/grasping-hands.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/death-gaze.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sorrow.jpg', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '16/15/14/13/12 seconds', '14/13/12/11/10 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '90 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy Gods\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"descriptio