(12, 'Ares', 'God of War', 'Greek', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/ares.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/ares.jpg', 'Shackles', 'Bolster Defenses', 'Searing Flesh', 'No Escape', 'Blessed Presence', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shackles.jpg', 'Chains extend from Ares\' shield, doing damage to all enemies in its path. Hitting a god shackles them to Ares, Cripples them, preventing movement abilities, dealing the same damage every second while slowing them by 15% and buffing Ares. While shackled, Ares can fire another chain for free within 2s.', 'Ares strengthens the defenses of himself and all nearby allies, granting Protections, HP5, and reducing Crowd Control durations. For each shackled enemy, the Protection Buffs are increased.', 'Flames pour forth from Ares\' shield, engulfing enemies in a cone in front of him causing damage every .5s for 4s.  Ares is immune to Knockback for the duration.', 'Ares throws chains out to all enemy gods in an area around him. All enemies hit by the chains are pulled to Ares after 2.5s, taking damage and are Stunned.', 'Each completed aura item that Ares owns grants him 30 additional Magical Power.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/bolster-defenses.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/searing-flesh.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/no-escape.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/blessed-presence.jpg', '15 seconds', '15 seconds', '12 seconds', '100 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '80/85/90/95/100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self/Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"35\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone