(13, 'Artemis', 'Goddess of the Hunt', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/artemis.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/artemis.jpg', 'Transgressor\'s Fate', 'Vengeful Assault', 'Suppress the Insolent', 'Calydonian Boar', 'Still Target', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/transgressors-fate.jpg', 'Artemis places a trap on the ground. Enemy gods coming within 5 units of her traps activate them, Rooting and Crippling the enemy god, preventing movement abilities and dealing damage every second for 3s. ', 'Artemis attacks at a furious pace, increasing her Attack and Movement Speed significantly. Additionally, Artemis cleanses herself of slows and becomes immune to Slows for 0.6s when activated.', 'Artemis fires a volley into a ground target, suppressing all of her enemies. Enemies caught within the volley are damaged and are Slowed.', 'Artemis summons the great Calydonian Boar on her enemies, doing damage to the nearest enemy god and Stunning them, and itself. The boar is immune until it hits the first god and then continues to charge other gods for its lifetime. Artemis is also immune to Crowd Control for 1.5s.', 'Artemis deals 15% increased Basic Attack damage to gods and 30% to minions who are afflicted by Crowd Control. ', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vengeful-assault.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/suppress-the-insolent.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/calydonian-boar.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/still-target.jpg', '18/16/14/12/10 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '10 seconds', '90 seconds', '45 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy Gods\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"va