(15, 'Athena', 'Goddess of Wisdom', 'Greek', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/athena.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/athena.jpg', 'Preemptive Strike', 'Confound', 'Shield Wall', 'Defender of Olympus', 'Reach', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/preemptive-strike.jpg', 'Athena powers up for a dash. While dashing, Athena will pass through minions, stop and hit the first enemy god she encounters, dealing damage and slowing all she hits. If she hits an enemy, Athena gains one stack of Block (max 3), absorbing the next Basic Attack from any god that hits her.', 'Athena releases a shockwave of power from her shield, Taunting enemy gods, and forcing them to fight or chase her.', 'Athena summons a group of Athenian warriors who do damage upon arrival, and after 2s strike for additional damage.', 'Athena picks a single allied god anywhere in the world, and launches herself up into the air, landing next to that god 3.6 seconds later. During that 3.6 seconds, the allied god gains 30% Damage Mitigation. Enemies nearby when Athena lands take damage.', 'After using any ability, Athena\'s next Basic Attack is a ranged attack, hitting all enemies it passes through, and dealing an additional +15% of her Magical Power as damage. Reach\'s damage will trigger Basic Attack Item Effects, but not Ability ones.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/confound.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shield-wall.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/defender-of-olympus.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/reach.jpg', '14 seconds', '18 seconds', '14 seconds', '110 seconds ', '60/70/80/90/100 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy god\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Global\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/130/180/230/280 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Amount:\",\"value\":\"25% \"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"2.25s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Taunt Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.0/1.25/1.5/1.75/2.0s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Initial Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/110/150/190/230 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Secondary Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/135/200/265/330 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"350/430/510/590/670 (+90% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Allied Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"30%\"}]', '[]'),
(16, 'Awilix', 'Goddess of the Moon', 'Mayan', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/awilix.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/awilix.jpg', 'Summon Suku', 'Feather Step', 'Moonlight Charge', 'Gravity Surge', 'Initiative', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/summon-suku.jpg', 'Awilix mounts her Panther Suku, gaining movement speed but decreasing strafe speed. Awilix may leap off of Suku to deal damage to all enemies in the target area.\n\nCanceling this ability before leaping will not trigger its Cooldown.', 'Awilix flips over the last enemy she hit within 1.5s, Rooting, Crippling, and dealing damage as she passes over them. The damage dealt is modified based on the next attack in Awilix\'s Basic Attack progression.\n\nIf the next attack is her third attack, then she also hits all targets in the area around her.', 'Suku comes to Awilix\'s aid, rushing forward and damaging all enemies. If hit from the side or behind, enemies are also knocked up into the air.', 'Awilix calls upon the power of the moon, immediately pulling to her the closest enemy god she is facing that is either leaping or knocked up into the air. The target god takes damage when they land.\n\nAwilix is then bathed in moonlight, gaining bonus Attack Speed and Physical Power, along with protection against Roots, Slows, and Knockbacks for 6s.', 'If Awilix has not taken or dealt damage in the last 5s and she strikes an enemy first, she increases her Physical Power for a short duration.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/feather-step.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/moonlight-charge.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/gravity-surge.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/initiative.jpg', '15 seconds', '8 seconds', '12 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '30/35/40/45/50 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Mount, Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"30\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"70\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Stim\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"75\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/130/180/230/280 (+80% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Strafe cap:\",\"value\":\"275\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/85/120/155/190 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Progression Bonus:\",\"value\":\"1x/ 1.5x/ 2x\"},{\"description\":\"Root and Cripple Duration:\",\"value\":\"0.6s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/130/170/210/250 (+70% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"200/250/300/350/400 (80% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed:\",\"value\":\"30/40/50/60/70%\"},{\"description\":\"Physical Power:\",\"value\":\"20/30/40/50/60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Physical Power Increase:\",\"value\":\"30% for 2.5s\"}]'),
(17, 'BabaYaga', 'Witch of the Woods', 'Slavic', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/baba-yaga.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/baba-yaga.jpg', 'Wild Witchcraft', 'Baba\'s Brew', 'Blast Off!', 'Home Sweet Home', 'Creeping Cabin', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/wild-witchcraft.jpg', 'Baba Yaga throws forward magic imbued with chaotic qualities. The magic will travel in the path of a random shape (Left Corner, Right Corner, Split, or Oval) and leave behind a random magical field on the ground it flew over for 4s. The fields can boost friendly Protections, boost friendly Movement Speed, lower enemy Movement Speed, or Silence enemies.', 'Baba Yaga throws together random ingredients to brew a Potion. Each Eye of Newt increases the Potion\'s Damage by 7.5%. Each Dragon Scale adds a 12.5% slow to enemies hit for 2.5s. Each Wolf Tooth adds a 7.5% Attack Speed slow and Power reduction to enemies hit for 5s. Baba Yaga can store a single Potion in her consumable slot refiring/canceling this ability. She can pull it out at any time to throw it.', 'Baba Yaga crawls inside her Mortar for protection. While inside the mortar she gains Damage Mitigation, Knockup Protection, and begins to build up explosive magic. After 1s the magic explodes, launching Baba Yaga and her Mortar in the direction she is facing. Enemies near the Mortar when it explodes take damage.', 'Baba Yaga calls down her Cabin, causing it to crash onto her and launch nearby enemies away. Baba Yaga commands the cabin for up to 8s, using it as a protective shield to create and throw 4 Witchfire Bolts from the inside. When the thrown Witchfire lands, it explodes dealing damage to enemies in the area while leaving behind a creeping patch of fire that chases nearby enemies. Enemies caught in the creeping fire take burn damage every 0.4s.', 'Baba Yaga\'s Cabin accumulates up to 100 essence over time, when it moves, and if enemy gods get too close. Baba Yaga can approach the Cabin and use this essence to gain evolving item stacks. Items with a low stack count take more energy. If Baba Yaga has no stacking item this essence heals Baba Yaga for 0.8% max health per tick.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/babas-brew.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/blast-off.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/home-sweet-home.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/creeping-cabin.jpg', '12 seconds', '14 seconds', '16 seconds', '90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Random\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy/Ally\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Width:\",\"value\":\"5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"65\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/150/200/250/300 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protections:\",\"value\":\"15/20/25/30/35 for 1s\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"20/22.5/25/27.5/30% for 1s\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"20/22.5/25/27.5/30% for 1s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"85/120/155/190/225 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Ingredient Count:\",\"value\":\"3/3/4/4/5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/125/170/215/260 (+85% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"25/27.5/30/32.5/35%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Landing Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/145/190/235/280 (50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Burst Damage:\",\"value\":\"75/105/135/165/195 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Burn Damage:\",\"value\":\"12/17/22/27/32 (+10% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Shield Health:\",\"value\":\"160/230/300/370/440 (+15% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Item Stack Cost:\",\"value\":\"400 / Item Max Stacks\"},{\"description\":\"Heal Cost:\",\"value\":\"4\"}]'),
(18, 'Bacchus', 'God of Wine', 'Roman', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/bacchus.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/bacchus.jpg', 'Chug', 'Belly Flop', 'Belch of the Gods', 'Intoxicate', 'Drunk-O-Meter', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/chug.jpg', 'Bacchus takes a drink from his jug, giving him additional Buffs.', 'Bacchus jumps into the air and, not so gracefully, comes slamming to the ground belly first, knocking all enemies into the air and dealing damage. If he is Tipsy, all enemies are also Slowed after they land.', 'Bacchus lets out an obnoxiously loud belch, doing damage every .5s for 2s and Debuffing enemy healing. If he is Tipsy, enemies are Stunned for 1s. Bacchus is immune to knockback for the duration.', 'Bacchus smashes his jug of wine on the ground, intoxicating all nearby enemies and doing damage. If he is Smashed, Bacchus also gains a Magical Power Buff because of his anger over his lost wine!', 'Bacchus loves the drink and as Bacchus drinks from his jug, he becomes more intoxicated, gaining Buffs when he gets Tipsy and Smashed. Bacchus also celebrates when he kills an enemy god, giving him 10% on his meter.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/belly-flop.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/belch-of-the-gods.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/intoxicate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/drunk-o-meter.jpg', '10 seconds', '16 seconds', '14 seconds', '90 seconds', '40 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '95 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Drunk-O-Meter:\",\"value\":\"40%\"},{\"description\":\"Protections:\",\"value\":\"0/15/20/25/30/35\"},{\"description\":\"Magical Power:\",\"value\":\"0/7/14/21/28/35\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"6s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/130/170/210/250 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"20%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Tick:\",\"value\":\"25/40/55/70/85 (+15% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1s\"},{\"description\":\"Healing Debuff:\",\"value\":\"50%\"},{\"description\":\"Healing Debuff Duration:\",\"value\":\"4s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"250/325/400/475/550 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Intoxication Debuff Duration:\",\"value\":\"6s\"},{\"description\":\"Magical Power Buff:\",\"value\":\"20/30/40/50/60\"},{\"description\":\"Buff Duration:\",\"value\":\"5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Tipsy:\",\"value\":\"Gain 10 Magical Power and 5% Damage Mitigation\"},{\"description\":\"Smashed:\",\"value\":\"Gain 30 Magical Power and 10% Damage Mitigation\"}]'),
(19, 'Bakasura', 'the Great Devourer', 'Hindu', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/bakasura.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/bakasura.jpg', 'Take Down', 'Eat Minion', 'Butcher Blades', 'Regurgitate', 'Insatiable Hunger', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/take-down.jpg', 'Bakasura leaps to his ground target location, dealing damage to all enemies in the area and increases the damage they take from all sources by 10% for 3s.', 'Bakasura grabs a minion and devours it, healing himself and gaining a Protections Buff. Large Jungle monsters must be at 33% Health to be eaten, but will provide 2 minions toward Regurgitate. Up to 6 minions can be stored for Regurgitate.', 'Bakasura passively gains Physical Power. When activated, he gains additional true damage on each strike for the duration.', 'Bakasura regurgitates all of the minions consumed by his Eat Minion ability at his ground target location that Slows for 3s and Cripples enemy players. This area lasts for 5s. Bakasura\'s Basic Attacks become cone attacks and he is immune to Crowd Control for a short duration. Bakasura is able to use Eat Minion on his regurgitated minions.', 'Bakasura\'s attack and movement speed temporarily increases for each enemy that he kills.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/eat-minion.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/butcher-blades.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/regurgitate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/insatiable-hunger.jpg', '12 seconds', '15 seconds', '14 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '55 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Melee Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\