(20, 'BaronSamedi', 'God of Life and Death', 'Voodoo', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/baron-samedi.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/baron-samedi.jpg', 'Vivid Gaze', 'Consign Spirits', 'Wrap It Up', 'Life of the Party', 'Hysteria', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vivid-gaze.jpg', 'Baron Samedi animates two skulls, both which briefly warm up before firing two beams of voodoo magic that damage enemies. The beams crossover wherever Baron Samedi was aiming. Enemies hit by both beams take 15% damage on the second hit.\n\nIf the enemy god hit is above 30 Hysteria, their Physical Power, Magical Power, and Attack Speed are reduced.', 'Baron Samedi guides restless spirits to the ground and buries them. After a brief delay the ground erupts, damaging enemies standing in the area. If an enemy god is hit, friendly spirits fly from the area and heal allies near the explosion or by Baron Samedi.\n\nIf the enemy god hit is above 30 Hysteria the friendly spirit cleanses ally slow effects, and increases their Movement Speed.', 'Baron Samedi throws his snake forward, wrapping any enemy god hit and dealing damage every .5s for 2.5s and applying a ramp to root.\n\nIf a god hit is above 30 Hysteria, the snake will also lash out at nearby enemy gods who stand too close after 1s. Enemies hit by this are injected with venom that applies a ramp to root and deals the full damage over time immediately.', 'Baron Samedi pulls the souls of the living towards his Coffin, becoming immune to Crowd Control and taking 35% reduced damage. Enemy gods within range are caught in a Vortex, dragging them towards the Coffin and taking damage every .33s. When an enemy god gets too close to the Coffin their soul is ripped out, causing them to be stunned, take a large amount of damage based on their maximum health and gain max Hysteria. This ability persists for 3.5s or until an enemy god is pulled to the Coffin.\n\nIf targets being pulled are above 30 Hysteria, the pull strength is increased.', 'Baron shares Baron\'s Brew, a powerful restorative chalice, with his allies from the Item Shop. Enemies hit by Baron will have Hysteria applied to them. Baron\'s abilities interact with Hysteria to provide bonus effects. Targets at Max Hysteria take 20% additional damage from Baron Samedi.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/consign-spirits.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/wrap-it-up.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/life-of-the-party.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/hysteria.jpg', '9 seconds', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '14 seconds', '90 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy/Ally\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"18\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/130/170/210/250 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Power Reduction:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed Reduction:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Hysteria Per Hit:\",\"value\":\"10\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/125/180/235/290 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Flat Heal:\",\"value\":\"40/65/90/115/140 (+10% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Missing Health Heal:\",\"value\":\"10%\"},{\"description\":\"Ground Speed:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Hysteria Per Hit:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Per Tick:\",\"value\":\"10/18/26/34/42 (+8% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.75s\"},{\"description\":\"Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"0.75s\"},{\"description\":\"Hysteria Per Hit:\",\"value\":\"5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Per Tick:\",\"value\":\"17/24/31/38/45 (+6% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage On Hit:\",\"value\":\"100/170/240/310/380 (50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Max Health Damage:\",\"value\":\"10%\"},{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Hysteria Per Hit:\",\"value\":\"5\"}]', '[]'),
(21, 'Bastet', 'Goddess of Cats', 'Egyptian', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/bastet.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/bastet.jpg', 'Pounce', 'Razor Whip', 'Ensnaring Claw', 'Guardians of Bast', 'Tracking Scent', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/pounce.jpg', 'Bastet pounces to her target location, damaging enemies within the radius. For 4 seconds after pouncing, you can press the button again to pounce back to your initial location. Bastet moves 25% faster while in the return pounce state.\n\nIf Guardians of Bast is active, she will command her guardians to also pounce with her.', 'Bastet swipes at her enemies, causing them to Bleed for damage every second for the duration.\n\nIf Guardians of Bast is active, she will command her guardians to also swipe at her enemies.', 'Bastet sends a cat forward at her enemies. If a cat finds an enemy it ensnares them, damaging them and rooting them for .5s. The cat persists for 4s or until defeated, continuing to attack nearby enemies. The cats attacks will apply a 2s slow to the enemy.\n\nIf Guardians of Bast is active, she will command her guardians to also charge forward.', 'Bastet calls her loyal Guardian cats to her side. These Guardians will follow Bastet\'s order, assisting her in any ability she casts and dealing a percentage of Bastet\'s damage.', 'When Bastet hits an enemy she marks the target for a brief time. Marked targets leave behind a scent trail Bastet can follow, gaining Movement Speed while in the scent trail.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/razor-whip.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/ensnaring-claw.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/guardians-of-bast.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/tracking-scent.jpg', '12 seconds', '13 seconds', '12 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/85/90/95/100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",