(22, 'Bellona', 'Goddess of War', 'Roman', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/bellona.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/bellona.jpg', 'Shield Bash', 'Bludgeon', 'Scourge', 'Eagle\'s Rally', 'Master of War', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shield-bash.jpg', 'Bellona dashes forward and bashes with her shield, dealing damage and Slowing enemies. Bellona gains 1 Stack of block for each enemy god hit. Block absorbs all damage from a single Basic Attack and reflects a portion of the damage around her.\nBellona then makes Basic Attacks with sword and shield until she has not taken or dealt damage in the last 5s. Every 3 successful basic attacks she gains another Stack of block (max. 3).\n', 'Bellona summons a hammer and spins, hitting every enemy around her and then smashing forward in an overhand attack. Each enemy god hit in the spin increases the damage of the overhand attack.\n\nBellona now makes Basic Attacks with her hammer until she has not taken or dealt damage in the last 5s. Every hammer attack hits all enemies in melee range and only benefit from 33% of Bellona\'s total Lifesteal.', 'Bellona summons a scourge, dealing damage to all enemies in a line. Enemies hit are Disarmed, and cannot make Basic Attacks.\n\nBellona now makes Basic Attacks with a scourge until she has not taken or dealt damage in the last 5s. Basic Attacks have extended range (+4) and every third attack heals Bellona.', 'Bellona plants a Roman flag, granting Protections and increased Physical Power to allied gods. Enemies directly under where the flag is placed take damage and are Stunned for 1s.', 'Upon giving or receiving hits from Basic Attacks, Bellona gains Protections and movement speed for 4s. (max. 5 stacks).\n', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/bludgeon.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/scourge.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/eagles-rally.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/master-of-war.jpg', '15 seconds', '14/13/12/11/10 seconds', '20/19/18/17/16 seconds', '75 seconds', '60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies and Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"25\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Everyone\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"40\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/120/160/200/240 (+40% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Block Reflect:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"15/20/25/30/35% for 2s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Spin Damage:\",\"value\":\"30/60/90/120/150 (+25% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slam Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/130/190/250/310 (+60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slam Damage Increase:\",\"value\":\"25% per Enemy God hit\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/115/150/185/220 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Disarm Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.4/1.6/1.8/2/2.2s\"},{\"description\":\"Healing:\",\"value\":\"25/30/35/40/45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"140/230/320/410/500 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protections:\",\"value\":\"15/20/25/30/35\"},{\"description\":\"Physical Pow