(28, 'Chang\'e', 'Faerie of the Moon', 'Chinese', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/change.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/change.jpg', 'Crescent Moon Dance', 'Moonlit Waltz', 'Moonflower Dance', 'Waxing Moon', 'Jade Rabbit', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/crescent-moon-dance.jpg', 'Chang\'e flings a crescent moon in an arc, dealing damage to all enemies in its path.', 'Chang\'e performs an evasive spin dance. She is immune to damage and Crowd Control during the action. For each tick of damage from an ability or Basic Attack that was avoided, Chang\'e restores Mana to herself and her allies.', 'Chang\'e twirls, scattering flowers around her, and healing herself and all nearby allies and damaging nearby enemies. Moonflower Dance also reduces the healing of all nearby enemies.', 'Chang\'e\'s Waxing Moon dance is captivating, with this dance dealing damage and Stunning enemy gods in front of her.  Each subsequent god that gets Stunned is Stunned for longer than the previous one.', 'Chang\'e can purchase or sell items from anywhere and her Jade Rabbit companion will fetch them. When the Rabbit reaches the store then returns, the transaction completes. Only one item can be purchased or sold in this way at a time. Chang\'e also gains +25% movement speed with no backpedal penalty when using her dances.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/moonlit-waltz.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/moonflower-dance.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/waxing-moon.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/jade-rabbit.jpg', '6 seconds', '20/18.5/17/15.5/14 seconds', '12 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Arc\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Ally\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy and Ally\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/120/160/200/240 (+60% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Mana Restored:\",\"value\":\"20/30/40/50/60 per tick avoided\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Heal:\",\"value\":\"50/70/90/110/130 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"85/110/135/160/185 (+60% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Healing Reduction:\",\"value\":\"50%\"},{\"description\":\"Lifetime:\",\"value\":\"4s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"160/225/290/355/420 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1s + 1s for each god already Stunned\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dance Move Speed:\",\"value\":\"+25%\"}]'),
(29, 'Chernobog', 'Lord of Darkness', 'Slavic', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/chernobog.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/chernobog.jpg', 'Crystallized Curses', 'Vicious Barrage', 'Into Darkness', 'Living Nightmare', 'Heart of Cold', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/crystallized-curses.jpg', 'Chernobog conjures a large crystal of curses and hurls it at the target location dealing damage on landing. After several seconds the crystalline curses explode dealing damage again and rooting any enemy in the area. The crystal can be detonated early by firing at it with Vicious Barrage. ', 'Chernobog fires an enlarged crystal shard that can pierce enemies and deals damage like a Basic Attack.\nThis applies a single stack of Heart of Cold to all enemies it passes through and instantly detonates Crystallized Curses.\nAfter firing, Chernobog gains increased Attack Speed for several seconds.', 'Chernobog dashes forward, dealing damage and slowing any enemy he collides with for 2s. If Chernobog comes in contact with a wall, he briefly enters it as a shadow, becoming untargetable and immune to damage for up to 3s.\r\nChernobog can leave the wall early by dashing or just stepping out of the wall. If he remains for the full duration, Chernobog will automatically dash out as his time expires.', 'During a brief channeling period, Chernobog summons shadows at the location of all enemies that last for 8s and apply a short stacking Slow.\r\nChernobog can select any of his shadow clones to fly towards. Once he reaches the location he takes the place of his shadow, refreshing his cooldowns, as well as temporarily obtaining damage mitigations and extra movement speed.', 'Every successful Basic Attack impales the enemy with a brittle crystal. Upon reaching 3 stacks of Heart of Cold, the enemy explodes for extra damage in an area around them (This damage does not trigger Item effects).', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vicious-barrage.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/into-darkness.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/living-nightmare.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/heart-of-cold.jpg', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '12 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '110 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '70 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile and Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies and Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"65\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Global\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"10\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/95/120/145/170 (+80% of your physical power)\"},{\"description\":\"Detonation Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/80/110/140/170 (+80% of your physical power)\"},{\"description\":\"Root:\",\"value\":\"1s\"},{\"description\":\"Detonation Duration:\",\"value\":\"3s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Attack Speed:\",\"value\":\"20/30/40/50/60%\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"3/3.5/4/4.5/5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/75/90/105/120 (+45% of your physical power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"25%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Buff Duration:\",\"value\":\"6s\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"1