(30, 'Chiron', 'The Great Teacher', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/chiron.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/chiron.jpg', 'Training Exercise', 'Masterful Shot', 'Giddyup!', 'Centaurus', 'Herbal Medicine', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/training-exercise.jpg', 'Chiron warns his teammates to evade the area, granting them .3s of Crowd Control Immunity so they can escape before it explodes and does damage to all enemies in the area.\n\nApplies Target Mark', 'Chiron passively marks his enemies as targets when he damages them with Basic Attacks, Training Exercise, or Centaurus, reducing their Physical Protections by 5%. He may activate this ability to fire seeking arrows at all marked targets within range, damaging and slowing them.', 'Chiron gallops forward damaging enemies, knocking up minions, and kicking enemy gods behind him.\nChiron may fire Basic Attacks while charging.', 'Chiron is transformed into a constellation, and can fire three long-distance shots, even through walls.\nIf Chiron would be killed during this ability, he does not die until he runs out of time or shots.  Killing an enemy with this ability when Chiron would have died returns him to life with health equal to the damage dealt instead.\n Applies target mark.', 'Every 12s Chiron collects herbs for a poultice. Each time he uses an ability, a poultice is consumed to heal himself or an ally within 30 units, based on who has the lowest health.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/masterful-shot.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/giddyup.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/centaurus.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/herbal-medicine.jpg', '13 seconds', '16 seconds', '16 seconds', '90 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '65 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"