(31, 'Chronos', 'Keeper of Time', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/chronos.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/chronos.jpg', 'Time Rift', 'Accelerate', 'Stop Time', 'Rewind', 'Time Lord', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/time-rift.jpg', 'Chronos creates a rift in time, damaging all enemies in the area.', 'Chronos accelerates himself over time, allowing him to move faster initially and gain speed over time. While active, his Attack Speed is increased. This ability also stops the Wheel of Time.\n\nSection I: Heal 1.5% Max Health Per Second.\nSection II: 100% Mana Refund On Abilities.\nSection III: +25% Magical Power.\nSection IV: +35% Magical Power Contribution to Basic Attacks.', 'Shooting forward spinning gears of time, any enemies hit by Chronos\' attack have their Attack Speed reduced and Ramp to a Stun, taking damage on the initial hit and again when they are stunned.', 'Chronos travels through time to where he was 8 seconds ago, gaining Health and Mana back to the values of that time.  All of his Cooldowns are instantly reset as well.', 'Chronos becomes empowered as time flows around him. Every 2 minutes he gains a stack that increases his Magical Power. Stacks up to 25 times, stacks are permanent.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/accelerate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/stop-time.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/rewind.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/time-lord.jpg', '5 seconds', '15 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '100/95/90/85/80 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '65/70/75/80/85 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"10\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\