(32, 'Cthulhu', 'The Great Dreamer', 'Great Old Ones', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/cthulhu.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/cthulhu.jpg', 'Sanity Break', 'The Mire', 'Rushing Terror', 'Descend into Madness', 'Prey on Fear', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sanity-break.jpg', 'Cthulhu sends out a terrifying blast of energy, dealing damage to all enemies hit and reducing their Attack Speed. Enemies hit by this ability also do reduced damage to Cthulhu for 6s.\nThis ability applies 1 stack of Torment, 2 if the enemy hit is facing Cthulhu or Fears them instead if they are afflicted with Insanity.\nSuccessfully consuming Insanity permanently increases the base mitigation of this ability.', 'Cthulhu summons a portal creating a slowing field of eldritch mire at the target location. While Cthulhu channels, The Mire continues to grow as the portal fires out two masses of corruption that hit and damage all enemies in the field.\nThe first shot also Slows enemies while the second Roots them, both hits applying 1 stack of Torment. Cancelling the ability early stops The Mire from growing or the portal from firing additional shots.', 'Cthulhu creates two twisting projectiles at his sides as he unfurls his wings and charges forwards, damaging, stunning and knocking away enemies hit.\n\nThe projectiles follow at a slightly slower pace but travel further, damaging enemies as well.\n\nEnemies hit by Cthulhu or the projectiles gain 1 stack of Torment.', 'Cthulhu reveals his true form as he plunges the battlefield into R\'lyeh while any enemies caught nearby are damaged.\nIn this form Cthulhu gains increased Health, becomes immune to Crowd Control and gains access to new abilities. Enemies near Cthulhu gain stacks of Torment, increasing in pace if they are facing him. Enemies also suffer the debuff effects of Sanity Break, causing them to deal less damage to Cthulhu.\n<font color=\'#9932CC\'>Ph\'nglui mglw\'nafh Cthulhu R\'lyeh wgah\'nagl fhtagn.</font>', 'Cthulhu breaks down the mental fortitude of enemy gods, applying stacks of Torment with abilities and the final hit of his basic attack chain. On reaching 4 stacks of Torment, enemies are afflicted by Insanity. Additionally, Cthulhu gains Magical Power per nearby enemy god with Insanity.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/the-mire.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/rushing-terror.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/descend-into-madness.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/prey-on-fear.jpg', '10 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '16 seconds', '120 seconds', '60 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20-30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"50\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Stim\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"40\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"70\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/135/180/225/270 (+40% of your magical power)\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed Slow:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30% for 3s\"},{\"description\":\"Fear Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"20% + 0.5% (Max 30%)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per shot:\",\"value\":\"50/95/140/185/230 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"10%\"},{\"description\":\"Corruption Slow:\",\"value\":\"35%\"},{\"description\":\"Corruption Slow/Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"1s\"},{\"description\":\"Mire Duration:\",\"value\":\"3s after ability cancel/end\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/110/150/190/230 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun Duration:\",\"value\":\"0.4s\"},{\"description\":\"Projectile Damage:\",\"value\":\"40/70/100/130/160 (+20% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"160/205/250/295/340 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Max Health:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"10/11/12/13/14s\"},{\"description\":\"Debuff Radius:\",\"value\":\"50\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Torment Duration:\",\"value\":\"5s\"},{\"description\":\"Insanity Duration:\",\"value\":\"20s\"},{\"description\":\"Magical Power:\",\"value\":\"25 per enemy with Insanity\"}]'),
(33, 'CuChulainn', 'Hound of Ulster', 'Celtic', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/cu-chulainn.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/cu-chulainn.jpg', 'Barbed Spear (Ground Slam)', 'Vent Anger', 'Salmon\'s Leap (Furious Charge)', 'Spear of Mortal Pain (War Cry)', 'Berserk', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/barbed-spear.jpg', 'Cu Chulainn thrusts his spear forward, damaging all enemies in front of him and stunning less powerful minions. Successfully hitting an enemy minion with this ability restores 5 Rage, 8 for a god (to a max of 18). Barbs from his spear stick in opponents and reduce their healing received for 4s.\nIn his Berserk Form, Cu Chulainn instead slams his massive arms down, damaging and rooting all enemies in front of him and this ability costs no Rage.', 'Cu Chulainn vents his anger as superheated steam, increasing his Movement Speed and draining his Rage. Every .5s while in this state, all enemies within range are damaged by the heat. Vent Anger does not return Rage.\n\nIn his Berserk form, Cu Chulainn Vents Anger automatically and does not drain Rage.', 'Cu Chulainn vaults over his spear, leaping to a target location and slamming it down to damage enemies around and in front of him. Successfully hitting an enemy minion with this ability restores 5 Rage, 8 for a god (to a max of 18).\n\nIn his Berserk Form, Cu Chulainn instead charges forward damaging, stunning and driving all enemies back with him and this ability costs no Rage.', 'Cu Chulainn swings his spear Gae Bulg in a circle around him, Damaging and Knocking Up all Enemies. Successfully hitting an enemy minion with this ability restores 10 Rage, 26 for a god (to a max of 36).\n\nIn his Berserk Form, Cu Chulainn instead gives a terrifying yell, Damaging all Enemies and causing them to Tremble. This yell costs no Rage and has a 35s cooldown.', 'Cu Chulainn\'s Mana, MP5, and Mana Heals are applied to his Health pool. Abilities consume Rage, which stops regen at 25, but he gains Rage upon hitting with his Abilities as well as 1 Rage for Basic Attacks and .5 when he or allies take damage. After 3s above 85, he goes Berserk. While Berserk, Cu Chulainn gains Power and a Health Shield.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vent-anger.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/salmons-leap.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/spear-of-mortal-pain.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/berserk.jpg', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '6 seconds', '16 seconds', '85 seconds', '9 Rage mana', '16 Rage mana', '9 Rage mana', '14 Rage mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"22.5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"35\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"75/135/195/255/315 (+55% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Healing Reduction:\",\"value\":\"50%\"},{\"description\":\"Stun Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s\"},{\"description\":\"Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"1s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Tick:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30 (+5% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"5%\"},{\"descripti