(34, 'Cupid', 'God of Love', 'Roman', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/cupid.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/cupid.jpg', 'Heart Bomb', 'Share the Love', 'Flutter', 'Fields of Love', 'Lovestruck', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/heart-bomb.jpg', 'Cupid fires an arrow of love at the target, causing damage when it hits and Slowing them.  After a short time, the targets heart explodes, dealing the damage again to the target and all enemies within the radius. If Cupid has max Heart Stacks then all enemies in the explosion area are Stunned for 1s. Minions take 50% increased damage from Heart Bomb.', 'Cupid places 3 floating hearts at his ground target location that heal himself or allied gods when picked up. Cupid regenerates Mana for each heart that is picked up by an ally.', 'Passive: Cupid gains increased Attack Speed.\n\nActive: Cupid flutters forward quickly, leaving a trail behind him that increases all allies\' movement speed.', 'Cupid fires arrows of love at his ground target location, slowing enemies in the area and crippling them, preventing movement abilities. The arrows grow and explode, dealing damage and Mesmerizing enemies. Any damage done breaks the Mesmerize effect. If Cupid has max Heart Stacks the Mesmerize duration is doubled.', 'Every hit with a Basic Attack gives Cupid a Heart Stack that increases the damage or healing of his abilities. Heart Bomb and Fields of Love will always consume the Heart Stacks and at 8 Stacks they will have additional effects.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/share-the-love.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/flutter.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/fields-of-love.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/lovestruck.jpg', '12 seconds', '14 seconds', '16/15/14/13/12 seconds', '90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '50 mana', '70 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Proj