":\"200/250/300/350/400 (+60% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"1st Target Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s and AoE \"},{\"description\":\"Spread Targets Duration:\",\"value\":\"3s and Single Target \"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Physical Power:\",\"value\":\"5 + 2 per level \"},{\"description\":\"Magical Power:\",\"value\":\"10 + 3 per level \"}]'),
(37, 'ErlangShen', 'The Illustrious Sage', 'Chinese', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/erlang-shen.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/erlang-shen.jpg', 'Spot Weakness', 'Pin', '72 Transformations', '9 Turns Blessing', 'Howling Celestial Dog', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/spot-weakness.jpg', 'Erlang Shen opens his third eye and analyzes the enemy\'s strengths and weaknesses.  When activated, Erlang Shen gains additional Physical Damage on each strike.\n\nIf the buff effect has ended and the ability is on Cooldown, successful Basic Attacks reduce the Cooldown of this ability by 1s.', 'Erlang Shen launches a spear that damages enemies on impact.  Enemies in the dead center of the effect when it lands are Rooted in place.', 'Erlang Shen transforms into a Mink or Turtle and charges forward.\nMink: Damages all enemies, stopping on first god hit and increasing Attack Speed for 4s.\nTurtle: Knocks up all enemies in path and gains a health shield for 12s.', 'Erlang Shen Taunts nearby Enemy gods, gaining Damage Mitigation for the next 4s. Afterwards, if Erlang Shen is still alive he is Healed for a flat amount plus 15% of his Maximum Health.', 'Each time Erlang Shen hits an enemy with a Basic Attack, his dog hits as well for 15% of his Basic Attack power and 1% of the target\'s max. health. The percentage damage only works against gods and minions.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/pin.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/72-transformations.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/9-turns-blessing.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/howling-celestial-dog.jpg', '14 seconds', '16 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '85 seconds', '60 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '65/70/75/80/85 mana', '80/85/90/95/100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemies\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Physical Damage:\",\"value\":\"15/30/45/60/75 (+10% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"85/130/175/220/265 (+55% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.3s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Turtle Damage:\",\"value\":\"65/110/155/200/245 (+40% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Shield Health:\",\"value\":\"70/110/150/190/230 \"},{\"description\":\"Mink Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/130/190/250/310 (+85% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Mink Attack Speed:\",\"value\":\"15/20/25/30/35%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Heal:\",\"value\":\"150/225/300/375/450 (15% of your Maximum Health)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"10/11.25/12.5/13.75/15%\"},{\"description\":\"Taunt Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.2s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"(pexistsppropppower/0.15/+#/+15% of your Basic Attack Power)\"}]');
