(40, 'Freya', 'Queen of the Valkyries', 'Norse', 'Melee, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/freya.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/freya.jpg', 'Irradiate', 'Pulse', 'Banish', 'Valkyrie\'s Discretion', 'Brisingamen\'s Blessing', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/irradiate.jpg', 'Freya activates a Buff that makes her Basic Attacks do bonus Magical damage.', 'Freya activates a Buff that makes her Basic Attacks ranged, dealing bonus Magical damage and Slowing the target and all nearby enemies. The area effect and slow are lost when Irradiate is active.', 'At her ground target location, Freya Banishes her enemies into the air for a short time.  The enemies can\'t be hit or take action while in the air.', 'Freya uses her Cloak of Feathers to fly above the battlefield where she fires down blasts of Magical damage up to 4 times while flying. Freya can\'t be hit when at full ascension and can cancel it anytime.', 'Freya\'s necklace grants her additional Magical Lifesteal.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/pulse.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/banish.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/valkyries-discretion.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/brisingamens-blessing.jpg', '11 seconds', '11 seconds', '19/18/17/16/15 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '70/65/60/55/50 mana', '90/95/100/105/110 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"10\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Af