(47, 'Heimdallr', 'The Vigilant', 'Norse', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/heimdallr.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/heimdallr.jpg', 'Piercing Sight', 'Gjallarhorn', 'The Bifrost', 'Through The Realms', 'The Vigilant', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/piercing-sight.jpg', 'Heimdallr throws his sword, Hofu, into the air. It shines with brilliant light that reveals enemies within 80 units. Heimdallr can refire this ability to call the sword down, causing it to fly to the target location and damage enemies.', 'Heimdallr blows the Gjallarhorn for 2s, causing enemies in front of him to lose Movement and Attack Speed while taking damage every .5s. While blowing his horn Heimdallr is immune to knockups. When Heimdallr ends this cast, either through cancelling it himself or after 2s, he raises the Gjallarhorn for a final blast. This blast damages enemies and knocks them away from Heimdallr.', 'Heimdallr manifests a fragment of the Bifrost at his target location. When two fragments are placed they become linked, allowing Heimdallr to traverse the Bifrost. The greater the distance between the fragments the longer it takes to begin traversing and the longer it takes for it to be usable again. If Heimdallr places a third fragment down, the oldest fragment vanishes. Enemies that walk between two fragments are revealed to Heimdallr. ', 'Heimdallr charges forward, axe ready. If Heimdallr hits an enemy god he stuns them before unleashing a devastating swing of his axe, launching his target into the sky. A Bifrost portal appears and Heimdallr sends the launched foe through the realms of Muspelheim and Niflheim before returning them back to the battleground at a random location in front of him. Muspelheim burns the enemy every .5s for 1.5s while Niflheim slows the enemy for 2.5s.', 'When Heimdallr gains vision of an enemy god he gains Physical Power, up to a maximum of 5 gods. When an enemy god would disappear from vision (including Stealth) Heimdallr continues to see them for 4s. Heimdallr\'s Critical Strikes only deal 70% bonus damage.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/gjallarhorn.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/the-bifrost.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/through-the-realms.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/the-vigilant.jpg', '14 seconds', '14 seconds', 'Variable', '90 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '40 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"Unlimited\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/130/190/250/310 (+85% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Per Tick:\",\"value\":\"8/16/24/32/40 (+30% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Knockback Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/90/130/170/210 (+60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"15/17.5/20/22.5/25%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Distance Scale:\",\"value\":\"85 to 700 units\"},{\"description\":\"Warmup Scale:\",\"value\":\"0.8s to 3.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Cooldown Scale:\",\"value\":\"14s to 210/180/150/120/90s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Hit Damage:\",\"value\":\"120/200/280/360/440 (+70% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Muspelheim Damage:\",\"value\":\"25/35/45/55/65 (+15% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Wall Hit Damage:\",\"value\":\"35/75/115/155/195 (+30% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Niflheim Slow:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Travel Duration:\",\"value\":\"4s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Physical Power per Stack\",\"value\":\"2%\"}]'),
(48, 'Hel', 'Goddess of the Underworld', 'Norse', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/hel.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/hel.jpg', 'Decay (Restoration)', 'Hinder (Cleanse)', 'Repulse (Inspire)', 'Switch Stances (Light)', 'Stance Attunement', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/decay.jpg', 'DECAY (Dark Stance) - Hel fires an orb of decay that deals damage and passes through minions. The orb will explode in a 12 unit radius if it hits a god, a wall, or reaches max range.\n\nRESTORATION (Light Stance) - Hel fires an orb of restoration that hits gods only. Hitting an enemy god deals damage. Hitting an allied god heals that god and heals Hel on a successful hit.', 'HINDER (Dark Stance) - Hel debuffs all enemies in the targeted area, reducing their Magical Protection and slowing them for 3s.\n\nCLEANSE (Light Stance) - Hel cleanses all allied gods in the targeted area, removing all Crowd Control effects instantly and protecting them from future ones for a duration.', 'REPULSE (Dark Stance) - Hel conjures a burst of dark energy around her, damaging all nearby enemies.\n\nINSPIRE (Light Stance) - Hel conjures a burst of light energy around her, healing herself instantly and applying a heal over time to nearby allies that ticks every 1s. Hel gains Increased Movement Speed, and allies gain a reduced amount (10%) for the duration. ', 'DARK STANCE - Hel\'s abilities cause damage and she gains increased Magical Power.\n\nLIGHT STANCE - Hel\'s abilities heal and support her allies and she gains increased Protections.\n\nPassive - Hel gains increased MP5 and Half of the benefits gained from Switch Stances are shared with allied gods within 30 units.', 'When Hel is in a stance, she gradually attunes to the strengths of that stance, gaining up to 20% damage in the Dark Stance and 20% healing in the Light Stance.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/hinder.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/repulse.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/switch-stances.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/stance-attunement.jpg', '8 seconds', '16/15/14/13/12 seconds', '12 seconds', '2 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '0 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies or Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies or Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage: \",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies or Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dark Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/110/160/210/260 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Ally Heal:\",\"value\":\"60/90/120/150/180 (+25% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Self Heal: \",\"value\":\"60/90/120/150/180 (+25% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/110/160/210/260 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dark Protections Debuff:\",\"value\":\"5/10/15/20/25\"},{\"description\":\"Dark Slow:\",\"value\":\"20/25/30/35/40%\"},{\"description\":\"Light CC Immunity Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dark Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/130/180/230/280 (+70% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Self Heal: \",\"value\":\"60/90/120/150/180 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Heal per Tick:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30 (+5% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Light Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Light Duration:\",\"value\":\"6s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dark Magical Power:\",\"value\":\"30/40/50/60/70\"},{\"description\":\"Light Magical and Physical Protections:\",\"value\":\"13/16/19/22/25\"},{\"description\":\"MP5:\",\"value\":\"15/20/25/30/35\"}]', '[]'),
(49, 'Hera', 'Queen of the Gods', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/hera.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/hera.jpg', 'Royal Assault', 'Polymorph', 'Divine Shroud', 'Argus, the Defender', 'Commanding Presence', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/royal-assault.jpg', 'Hera damages enemies in a cone in front of her before opening a portal for Argus to attack through. Enemy minions hit by this cone are knocked into Argus\' path. Argus then slams his fists at the target location dealing heavy damage. If both of his fists connects with an enemy, it deals 15% extra damage.', 'Hera weaves magic in front of her before sending it out. Enemies hit by this ability take damage. If this ability hits a god it causes their form to shift into a monster.', 'Hera shrouds herself in her divine power, granting her a shield from damage and temporary movement speed that lasts as long as the shield remains.\n\nIf Argus is active, Argus shines with the same Divine power as Hera, causing him to deal radiant damage and move at an increased rate.', 'Hera brings Argus crashing down at a location, damaging and knocking up enemies. On landing Argus will attack the nearest target. Hera can control where Argus moves through refiring this ability onto an enemy or if he has a target, to recall him. While recalled Argus will defend Hera and attack anyone that gets close. Argus has a hit chain that starts with a normal basic attack, into a ground circle AoE slowing enemies by 20% for 1s, into a line attack.', 'Each time Hera deals damage to gods with her Abilities or Basic Attacks Argus, The Defender\'s cooldown is reduced by 1s and Divine Shroud\'s cooldown is reduced by 0.33s. If Argus is active he is instead healed.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/polymorph.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/divine-shroud.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/argus-the-defender.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/commanding-presence.jpg', '10 seconds', '14 seconds', '16 seconds', '90 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75  mana', '60 mana', '45/50/55/60/65 mana', '80/85/90/95/100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"AoE\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"80\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Shield and Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"AoE\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Pet\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Cone Damage:\",\"value\":\"30/40/50/60/70 (+15% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Fist Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/130/180/230/280 (+80% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/120/160/200/240 (+75% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Polymorph Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.2/1.4/1.6/1.8/2s\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"20%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Shield Health:\",\"value\":\"50/100/150/200/250 +15 per Hera\'s Level\"},{\"description\":\"Shield Duration:\",\"value\":\"5s\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"15%\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Aura Damage:\",\"value\":\"7/11/15/19/23 (/+7.5% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Speed:\",\"value\":\"50%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/150/200/250/300 (+55% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Lifetime:\",\"value\":\"40s\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Health:\",\"value\":\"700/1400/2100/2800/3500\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Protections:\",\"value\":\"25/30/35/40/45\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"440/455/470/485/500\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Argus Heal:\",\"value\":\"20 + 5 per level \"},{\"description\":\"Argus First Hit:\",\"value\":\"30 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Second Hit:\",\"value\":\"30 (+30% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Argus Third Hit:\",\"value\":\"45 (+40% of your Magical Power)\"}]'),
(50, 'Hercules', 'Champion of Rome', 'Roman', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/hercules.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/hercules.jpg', 'Driving Strike', 'Earthbreaker', 'Mitigate Wounds', 'Excavate', 'Strength from Pain', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/driving-strike.jpg', 'Hercules delivers a mighty strike, driving all enemies back, damaging and Stunning them. Hercules is immune to Knockback during the dash.', 'Hercules smashes the ground, sending a shockwave forward that does damage to all enemies in the path. Enemies at the end of the shockwave are thrown into the air towards Hercules.', 'Hercules heals himself instantly and gains increased Magical and Physical Protections for the next 4s. A percentage of the damage taken during this time is returned to him as an additional heal at the end of the duration.', 'Hercules rips a huge boulder from the ground. Throwing the boulder does damage where the boulder lands. The boulder continues rolling, doing the same damage to all enemies in its path. Subsequent hits on the same enemy do 50% less damage per hit. Hercules is immune to Crowd Control while casting.', 'Every time Hercules takes damage from an enemy god he gains a stacking self buff that provides increased Physical Power.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/earthbreaker.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mitigate-wounds.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/excavate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/strength-from-pain.jpg', '14 seconds', '14 seconds', '17 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage: