(51, 'Horus', 'The Rightful Heir', 'Egyptian', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/horus.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/horus.jpg', 'Updraft', 'Fracture', 'Protector\'s Surge', 'To The Skies!', 'Resolute', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/updraft.jpg', 'Horus uses his wings to create an updraft around himself, knocking nearby enemies into the air.\n\nUsing the currents from the updraft, Horus\' next Basic Attack within 5s will create a gust of wind that travels forward, damaging enemies and slowing them for 2.5s. This attack cannot crit. Enemies that are knocked up when hit take bonus damage.', 'Horus dashes forward a short distance, ready to strike with his weapon. If Horus hits a god he stops and stuns the god for 1.25s. He will then wind up a heavy cleave. Enemies hit have their Protections reduced for 3s. ', 'Horus rushes to the aid of an ally. After selecting an ally, Horus will fly to their location before descending. Upon landing, the selected ally and all nearby allies have their health restored and gain protections for 3s.', 'Horus sends a mirror image of himself into the sky that scouts for a location to fly to. Upon selecting a ground location, Horus will begin to channel for 2s. Allies near Horus after these 2 seconds are flown to the location Horus\' image chose. Horus and his allies land with such force, enemies take damage and are knocked away from the landing location. Horus and allies at the landing location gain a protective shield.', 'Each time Horus is damaged by an enemy god, Horus gains a stack of Resolute. If Set is the god damaging Horus, Horus gains 2 stacks. Each stack increases Horus\' Protections and CCR. Resolute stacks to a max count of 10 for 3s. When Resolute fades, Horus is healed based on the amount of stacks. ', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/fracture.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/protectors-surge.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/to-the-skies.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/resolute.jpg', '16/16/15/15/14 seconds', '16/15.5/15/14.5/14 seconds', '16 seconds', '100 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '65 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"12\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"35\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Teleport\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/95/140/185/230 (+60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Gust Damage:\",\"value\":\"14/23/32/41/50 +100% of your Basic Attack Damage\"},{\"description\":\"Gust Bonus Damage:\",\"value\":\"1.5x\"},{\"description\":\"Gust Slow:\",\"value\":\"25%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Dash Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/95/120/145/170 (+30% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Cleave Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/95/120/155/190 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protection Reduction:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Heal:\",\"value\":\"50/100/150/200/250 (+10% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protection Buff:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"150/250/350/450/550 (+80% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Shield:\",\"value\":\"160/240/320/400/480\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Protections per Stack:\",\"value\":\"1.5\"},{\"description\":\"CCR per Stack:\",\"value\":\"1.5%\"},{\"description\":\"Heal per Stack:\",\"value\":\"2 +0.75 per Level\"}]'),
(52, 'HouYi', 'Defender of the Earth', 'Chinese', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/hou-yi.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/hou-yi.jpg', 'Ricochet', 'Mark of the Golden Crow', 'Divebomb', 'Sunbreaker', 'Suntouched', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/ricochet.jpg', 'Hou Yi fires a powerful shot that can ricochet off of walls. After firing, if this arrow bounces off of a wall it will travel 70 units from that point and gain +40% bonus damage to gods per bounce up to a maximum of 2 bounces. This arrow will stun if the target has Mark of the Golden Crow.', 'Hou Yi marks an enemy with Mark of the Golden Crow. Marked enemies take extra damage for every 10% of their missing health from Hou Yis abilities and basic attacks. Also, marked enemies, including stealthed gods, are visible to Hou Yi on the minimap. The mark lasts for 10s.', 'Hou Yi launches into the air, and for a short time may target some distance away to quickly dive towards the ground damaging any enemies in the immediate area. If the target has Mark of the Golden Crow they are knocked back.', 'Hou Yi shoots nine arrows into the sky, striking one sun with each arrow. The nine suns come crashing down one by one, slowing and dealing damage in a target area over time. A target with Mark of the Golden Crow will have their movement speed slowed by an additional 20%.', 'After taking a critical hit, Hou Yi cant be critically hit again for 3s.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mark-of-the-golden-crow.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/divebomb.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sunbreaker.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/suntouched.jpg', '10 seconds', '18 seconds', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '50 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\