(55, 'Izanami', 'Matron of the Dead', 'Japanese', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/izanami.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/izanami.jpg', 'Sickle Storm', 'Spectral Projection', 'Fade Away', 'Dark Portal', 'Death Draws Nigh', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sickle-storm.jpg', 'For 6s, Izanami throws her kama sickles even faster and more furiously. While active she gains Attack Speed, and her Basic Attacks no longer return to her, instead applying Bonus Damage in addition to 100% of her Basic Attack power per hit. This Bonus Damage applies to all targets, including Structures.', 'Izanami sends forth a demonic visage of herself to strike down her enemies, damaging and Slowing all Enemies in a line.\n\nIf an Enemy God is killed while slowed by this ability, future uses of the slow will be increased by 6% per kill up to twice, for a maximum of 30%.', 'Izanami descends into the underworld, becoming Stealthed, and leaps away from her current position.\n\nTaking damage, or firing a damaging Ability or Basic Attack breaks her Stealth.', 'Izanami summons a dark portal which Damages and Silences all Enemies in range.', 'The closer Izanami gets to death, the more powerful she becomes.  Izanami gains 4% Physical Penetration for each 10% of her Health that is missing, up to a maximum of 20%.\nAlso, Izanami\'s Basic Attacks only trigger Item effects on the first target hit per attack.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/spectral-projection.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/fade-away.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/dark-portal.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/death-draws-nigh.jpg', '10 seconds', '14/13.5/13/12.5/12 seconds', '20/19/18/17/16 seconds', '80', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '70 mana', '70 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\