(61, 'KingArthur', 'Wielder of Excalibur', 'Arthurian', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/king-arthur.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/king-arthur.jpg', 'Overhead Slash (Hamstring)', 'Battle Stomp (Uppercut)', 'Twin Cleave (Bladestorm)', 'Sundering Strike (Excalibur\'s Wrath)', 'Steadfast', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/overhead-slash.jpg', 'Standard: King Arthur deals a devastating overhead blow in Melee range that creates a slashing attack that travels forwards. Enemies hit by the Melee strike take bonus damage from the Slicing attack.\r\n\r\nCombo: King Arthur swipes low, crippling and damaging enemies that are struck.', 'Standard: King Arthur stomps on the ground with heavy force, causing enemies around him to take damage and become slowed.\r\nCombo: King Arthur charges forward, stopping on first god hit. At the end of the charge King Arthur unleashes an uppercut, knocking up enemies into the air.', 'Standard: King Arthur unleashes two cleave attacks while charging forward. Enemies hit by a cleave take damage and have their protections reduced.\r\nCombo: King Arthur swings Excalibur around him, charging forward and damaging enemies 5 times before winding up a final strike that deals more damage. King Arthur is immune to Knockup for the duration.', '35 Energy: King Arthur winds up a massive jab, charging forwards slightly before striking. Enemies hit by this jab are stunned for 1s. 80 Energy: King Arthur charges forward with Excalibur drawn. If King Arthur hits an enemy god, he launches them into the air and unleashes a barrage of 6 attacks, after which he launches them back to the ground dealing damage to the target and any enemy below.', 'Each ability that damages a god results in a stack of Steadfast, reducing damage taken and increasing energy gain. Each time King Arthur uses an ability he swaps between his Standard and Combo Abilities. All abilities are Instant Cast. Attack Speed and Item Passives do not benefit his Basic Attacks. Attack Speed increases his energy gain.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/battle-stomp.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/twin-cleave.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sundering-strike.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/steadfast.jpg', '14 seconds', '14 seconds', '16 seconds', '20', '35/40/45/50/55 mana', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '35 (80) Energy & 40 Mana mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line (Cone)\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"70 (30)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle (Dash)\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"20 (35)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"AoE (Dash)\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"10 (20)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line (Dash)\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45 (35)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Slash Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/115/170/225/280 (60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Melee Bonus Damage:\",\"value\":\"30/35/40/45/50%\"},{\"description\":\"Combo Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/120/180/240/300 (+60% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Cripple Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.25s\"},{\"description\":\"Energy Gain:\",\"value\":\"3\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Stomp Damage:\",\"value\":\"40/65/90/115/140 (40% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"20/25/30/35/40%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"2.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Uppercut Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/95/140/185/230 (40% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Energy Gain:\",\"value\":\"4\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Cleave Damage:\",\"value\":\"35/60/85/110/135 (30% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protection Shred:\",\"value\":\"7%\"},{\"description\":\"Spin Damage:\",\"value\":\"10/30/50/70/90 (+15% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Final Damage:\",\"value\":\"30/80/130/180/230 (40% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Energy Gain:\",\"value\":\"1.5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Jab Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/160/220/280/340 (+65% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Per Hit:\",\"value\":\"10/25/40/55/70 (+10% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Max HP Damage:\",\"value\":\"2%\"},{\"description\":\"Landing Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/110/170/230/290 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Max HP Damage:\",\"value\":\"5/7/9/11/13% Landing Hit\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"1.5% per Stack\"},{\"description\":\"Bonus Energy Gain:\",\"value\":\"20% per Stack\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"15s\"},{\"description\":\"Max Stacks:\",\"value\":\"4\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed Conversion:\",\"value\":\"33%\"}]'),
(62, 'Kukulkan', 'Serpent of the Nine Winds', 'Mayan', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/kukulkan.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/kukulkan.jpg', 'Zephyr', 'Slipstream', 'Whirlwind', 'Spirit Of The Nine Winds', 'Power Of The Wind Jewel', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/zephyr.jpg', 'Kukulkan fires a projectile breath attack that hits the first enemy in its path, doing damage and Slowing all enemies in the area around the impact.', 'Kukulkan channels the wind, allowing him to move faster. This speed boost is strong at first but scales down gradually over the 4s duration. Additionally, Kukulkan cleanses himself of slows and becomes immune to Slows for 0.6s when activated.', 'Kukulkan summons a tornado at his ground target location. A smaller tornado branches off onto any enemies that come within the radius, doing damage every .5s for 2.5s and is refreshed if enemies stay within the radius, for a maximum of 12 ticks.', 'Kukulkan summons the Spirit Of The Nine Winds to breathe down destruction onto his enemies in a path in front of him, doing damage and knocking all of the enemies to the side.', 'Increases Magical Power by 4% of maximum Mana.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/slipstream.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/whirlwind.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/spirit-of-the-nine-winds.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/power-of-the-wind-jewel.jpg', '7 seconds', '15 seconds', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '65 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '100/110/120/130/140 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affect