(63, 'Kumbhakarna', 'The Sleeping Giant', 'Hindu', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/kumbhakarna.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/kumbhakarna.jpg', 'Throw Back', 'Groggy Strike', 'Mighty Yawn', 'Epic Uppercut', 'Sleepy', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/throw-back.jpg', 'Kumbhakarna sleepily runs forward. If he hits an enemy he stops and deals damage. If the enemy is a minion, he throws them, dealing increased damage to each enemy they hit.', 'Kumbhakarna smashes down, damaging all enemies in front of him and Rooting them.', 'Kumbhakarna lets out a mighty yawn that Mesmerizes all enemies in range. If awakened early, enemies have their Attack Speed and Movement Speed Slowed. Kumbhakarna may use this ability while asleep.', 'Kumbhakarna moves forward, stops at the first enemy god he encounters, and delivers a massive melee attack that uppercuts the enemy directly into the air. When the enemy lands, it deals area damage and causes Knockup to enemies nearby.', 'Kumbhakarna does not die when he reaches 0 Health, instead he falls asleep. He will awaken after 8s at 25% Health and Mana, unless hit with 6 Basic Attacks (+1 every 5 levels) while sleeping. This passive has a 240s Cooldown.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/groggy-strike.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mighty-yawn.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/epic-uppercut.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sleepy.jpg', '13 seconds', '10 seconds', '15 seconds', '75 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"40\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"25\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"30\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/140/210/280/350 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Flying Minion Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/160/230/300/370 (+60% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"90/140/190/240/290 (+50% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Mez Duration:\",\"value\":\"1/1.5/2/2.5/3s\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"1/1.25/1.5/1.75/2s\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"40%\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed Debuff:\",\"value\":\"30/35/40/45/50%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Initial Damage:\",\"value\":\"75/100/125/150/175 (+15% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Landing Damage:\",\"value\":\"200/290/380/470/560 (+40% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Knockup Time:\",\"value\":\"2.2s\"}]', '[]'),
(64, 'Kuzenbo', 'King Kappa', 'Japanese', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/kuzenbo.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/kuzenbo.jpg', 'NeNe Kappa', 'Shell Spikes', 'Sumo Slam', 'Watery Grave', 'Water Bowl', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/nene-kappa.jpg', 'Kuzenbo summons and throws the powerful NeNe Kappa, who can ricochet off of walls. After firing, if the NeNe Kappa bounces off of a wall it will travel 70 units from that point up to a maximum of 2 bounces. After reaching maximum range, or if an Enemy God is hit by the NeNe Kappa, it will burst forth from its shell, slowing and attacking them for 6s. Kuzenbo transfers 20% of his Health and Protections to the NeNe Kappa.', 'The spikes on Kuzenbos back extend out, damaging enemies who attack Kuzenbo. While active, each time Kuzenbo takes damage, the cooldown on NeNe Kappa and Sumo Slam is reduced. Kuzenbo may activate this ability even while under the effects of Crowd Control.', 'Kuzenbo charges forward, immune to slows, damaging Enemy minions and silencing using his immense strength to push the first Enemy God he hits along with him. Each subsequent Enemy he hits deals damage to both that Enemy and the god Kuzenbo is pushing. Colliding with a wall will also deal damage to the pushed god. Pushed targets can be hit a maximum of 3 times.', 'Kuzenbo pulls himself inwards under his shell and spins, summoning fierce currents that knock enemies back, increase his movement speed, render him immune to Crowd Control, and allow him to move freely in all directions for 2.1s. Damage after the first spin is reduced by 50%.', 'Each time Kuzenbo takes over 2% of his maximum health worth of damage, pre-mitigation, he is granted stacks of Damage Mitigation as his head fills with water (Max 10 Stacks).  Stacks last 30s and refresh when he gains another. If he is knocked up, grabbed, pulled, banished or otherwise disrupted, the bowl loses half of its stacks.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shell-spikes.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sumo-slam.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/watery-grave.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/water-bowl.jpg', '16 seconds', '14/13.5/13/12.5/12 seconds', '12 seconds', '75 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '50 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Pet\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"70\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"22.5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/105/140/175/210 (+55% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Kappa Damage per Hit:\",\"value\":\"35/45/55/65/75\"},{\"description\":\"Kappa Health:\",\"value\":\"25/30/35/40/45 (20% of your Maximum Health)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"20%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"3s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"% of Damage Taken:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30%\"},{\"description\":\"Cooldown per Hit:\",\"value\":\".5/.7/.9/1.1/1.3s\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"3s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Hit:\",\"value\":\"60/95/130/165/200 (+35% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage first Hit:\",\"value\":\"80/130/180/230/280 (40% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage per Hit:\",\"value\":\"40/65/90/115/140 (20% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"45%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"1.5% per 2% of Maximum Health taken\"},{\"description\":\"Maximum Mitigation:\",\"value\":\"15%\"},{\"description\":\"Mitigation Lost:\",\"value\":\"5 stacks\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"30s\"}]'),
(65, 'Loki', 'The Trickster God', 'Norse', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/loki.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/loki.jpg', 'Vanish', 'Agonizing Visions', 'Flurry Strike', 'Assassinate', 'Behind You!', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vanish.jpg', 'Loki disappears in a puff of smoke. While invisible, he moves faster, removes Slow effects, and gains immunity to Slow effects. His next Basic Attack from Stealth (or for 2s after) applies a Bleed to his target, dealing damage every .5s and reveals Loki. If Loki takes damage while in stealth he will be revealed for .33s.', 'Loki summons a vision of his tortured past at a target location for 4s. Enemies in range of the vision feel the poison themselves, taking damage and having their Damage Dealt reduced. This effect stacks up to 4 times. If an enemy gets 4 stacks they become Blinded, allowing Loki to benefit from Behind You! from any direction for 3s.', 'Loki unleashes a flurry of 5 dagger strikes quickly in front of him, damaging and slowing enemies by 15% for 3s. After this flurry he winds up for a final heavy strike that deals higher damage and slowing enemies by 30% for 3s. Loki cannot be knocked up while firing this ability. This ability can benefit from Behind You!', 'Upon activation, Loki teleports to his ground target location. If an enemy god is within the radius, Loki will slice that target doing damage and crippling them for 1s. After he teleports he will wind up a heavier strike, damaging all enemies in front of him and stunning them. ', 'Loki deals more damage from his Basic Attacks when hitting enemies from behind. His Basic Attacks also utilize a 5 swing progressive chain.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/agonizing-visions.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/flurry-strike.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/assassinate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/behind-you.jpg', '15 seconds', '12', '12', '90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Melee Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"25\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Teleport\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy Gods\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Tick:\",\"value\":\"30/45/60/75/90 (+25% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Duration:\",\"value\":\"2s\"},{\"description\":\"Stealth Duration:\",\"value\":\"4s\"},{\"description\":\"Stealth Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"35%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"13/18/23/28/33 (+15% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage Dealt:\",\"value\":\"5% for 2.5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Flurry Damage:\",\"value\":\"19/28/37/46/55 (+18% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Final Damage:\",\"value\":\"40/65/90/115/140 (+60% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Cripple Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/105/140/175/210 (+35% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Heavy Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/145/190/235/280 (90% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Bonus Damage:\",\"value\":\"20%\"}]'),
(66, 'Medusa', 'The Gorgon', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/medusa.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/medusa.jpg', 'Viper Shot', 'Acid Spray', 'Lacerate', 'Petrify', 'Sidewinder', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/viper-shot.jpg', 'Medusa gains increased attack speed and her basic attacks become augmented, shooting Vipers that poison the targets hit dealing damage over time.', 'Medusa hurls back and spits out acid that damages the first enemy hit and sprays out acid in a cone behind them. Acid Spray will explode on statues Medusa has created.', 'Medusa quickly slithers forward rooting and slashing the first enemy god she encounters. The slash leaves the enemy god reeling in pain, reducing their healing for a short time.', 'Medusa removes her mask revealing her true face, delivering a powerful blast from her horrifying Gorgon gaze. Enemies take damage and are stunned if they are looking at Medusa. Enemies not looking at Medusa take 75% damage and are slowed. Enemy gods that are killed during Medusa\'s gaze will turn to a stone statue and remain behind as a reminder to others.', 'Medusa suffers no movement penalty when side strafing and half of the movement penalty when moving backward.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/acid-spray.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/lacerate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/petrify.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sidewinder.jpg', '10 seconds', '14 seconds ', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '60/65/70/75/80  mana', '70 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self, Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",