(67, 'Mercury', 'Messenger of the Gods', 'Roman', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/mercury.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/mercury.jpg', 'Made You Look', 'Maximum Velocity', 'Special Delivery', 'Sonic Boom', 'Fastest God Alive', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/made-you-look.jpg', 'Mercury moves in the blink of an eye, dealing one melee attack to every enemy within the target area. This ability can Critically Hit, and triggers Ability related Item effects, not Basic Attack related Item effects. ', 'Passive: Mercury gains increased movement speed.\n\nActive: Mercury increases his Attack Speed, cleanses himself of Slows and becomes immune to Slows for the duration.', 'Mercury dashes forward, knocking aside minions, grabbing the first enemy god he encounters and spinning them. The enemy god takes damage until the effect ends, and Mercury throws the god in the direction of his choice.', 'Mercury gathers energy for a powerful Dash, with the range extending as he does so. He travels the distance faster than the speed of sound, dealing damage to all enemies, stunning them and spinning them around in a random direction.', 'For every 1 unit traveled, Mercury gains a 0.08% Physical Power bonus on his next Basic Attack (max 40%).\n\nMercury also gains additional Physical Power equal to 25% of movement speed from items or abilities.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/maximum-velocity.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/special-delivery.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sonic-boom.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/fastest-god-alive.jpg', '8 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '50 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical Basic Attack\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/105/140/175/210 (/+60% of your Basic Attack Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"7.5/9/10.5/12/13.5\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ground Speed:\",\"value\":\"2/4/6/8/10%\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Speed:\",\"value\":\"30/40/50/60/70%\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Minion Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/115/160/205/250 (+80% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Damage per Tick:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30 (+20% of your Physical Power) every 0.25s\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"1s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"200/275/350/425/500 (+100% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Disorient Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"}]', '[]'),
(68, 'Merlin', 'The Master Wizard', 'Arthurian', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/merlin.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/merlin.jpg', 'Eclipse (Radiate/Frostbolt)', 'Vortex (Dragonfire/Blizzard)', 'Flicker', 'Elemental Mastery', 'Overload', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/eclipse.jpg', 'Merlin conjures an orb of condensed celestial energy that grows in size as it travels, dealing damage every 0.4s and marking Enemies hit.\n\nEnemies marked take additional damage if they stay within the outer range of Eclipse.\n\n(Change stance to Fire/Ice for more information)', 'Merlin deploys a field of arcane energy at a location. After a delay, the Vortex deals damage and pulls Enemies towards the center.\n\n(Change stance to Fire/Ice for more information)', 'Merlin quickly teleports a short distance in front of him.', 'Merlin taps into his inner potential, exploding with energy in the stance he is currently attuned to. During this time Merlin can choose which stance to enter into next. \n\nAfter the explosion reaches its apex, it collapses in on itself. Enemies are dealt damage from the both the explosion and the implosion and suffer different effects depending on which stance\'s energy they are being hit by.', 'Every time Merlin casts a spell he gains a stack of Overload. When Merlin next fires a basic attack it will be augmented with lightning, dealing extra damage to the first Enemy.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/vortex.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/flicker.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/elemental-mastery.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/overload.jpg', '14 seconds', '16/15/14/13/12 seconds', '24/23/22/21/20 seconds', '32/29/26/23/20 seconds', '60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '70 mana', '40/50/60/70/80 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\