(74, 'Nox', 'Goddess of Night', 'Roman', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/nox.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/nox.jpg', 'Shadow Lock', 'Siphon Darkness', 'Shadow Step', 'Night Terror', 'Flame of the Night', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shadow-lock.jpg', 'Nox extends her shadow forward, damaging enemies. If this shadow hits an enemy god it stops, rooting and crippling them in place and dealing damage over time instead. Nox must channel and stay within range to maintain hold on the target, but may cancel this ability early. Nox will continue to channel this ability even if she is hit by Crowd Control effects. While channeling this ability Nox suffers no directional movement penalty.', 'Nox creates a void of darkness that silences all enemies within. After a short duration it explodes, dealing damage.', 'Nox dashes forward, dealing damage to all enemies. If she hits an allied god, she leaps into their shadow, traveling with them. When Nox exits a shadow, she deals damage again in a radius around her. Nox may cancel this ability early to exit shadows.', 'Nox unleashes a vortex of dark energy that explodes on contact with an enemy god, dealing damage to all enemies in range 20 and applying damage over time. Enemies hit are also weakened, dealing less damage for the duration.', 'Noxs candles gather energy from all abilities she uses. For every ability Nox casts, a candle is lit. For every candle lit Nox gains +3% magical power. When Nox takes damage from an enemy god one of her candles is blown out.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/siphon-darkness.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shadow-step.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/night-terror.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/flame-of-the-night.jpg', '10 seconds', '13 seconds', '15 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '90 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"descript