(81, 'Poseidon', 'God of the Oceans', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/poseidon.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/poseidon.jpg', 'Tidal Surge', 'Trident', 'Whirlpool', 'Release the Kraken!', 'Changing Tides', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/tidal-surge.jpg', 'Poseidon summons forth a wave that travels in a line, dealing damage and pushing back all enemies in its path.', 'Poseidon activates his Trident, granting movement speed and making his Basic Attacks fire 2 additional shots in a spread for 6s. The shots deal Magical damage plus 20% of Poseidon\'s Magical Power. All shots increase Poseidon\'s Tide on successful hit.', 'Poseidon summons a whirlpool at his ground target location that Cripples targets, preventing movement abilities, and creating a Vortex which drags targets toward the center dealing damage every .5s for 3s.', 'Poseidon releases the Kraken, damaging and Slowing targets in its radius. Enemies in the center of the effect when it spawns take additional damage, are Knocked Up and Stunned.', 'Poseidon\'s movement speed increases and his abilities do additional damage as his Tide Level increases. Successful Basic Attack hits increase his Tide, and using abilities decreases it.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/trident.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/whirlpool.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/release-the-kraken.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/changing-tides.jpg', '10 seconds', '20/18/16/14/12 seconds', '15/14/13/12/11 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '65/70/75/80/85 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100/110/120/130/140 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Abilit