(82, 'Ra', 'Sun God', 'Egyptian', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/ra.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/ra.jpg', 'Celestial Beam', 'Divine Light', 'Solar Blessing', 'Searing Pain', 'Speed of Light', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/celestial-beam.jpg', 'Ra summons a moving beam of intense light from the sky, doing damage to anyone caught under the beam.', 'Light starts to emanate from Ra, Stacking a Slow every .5s on enemies near him, and twice as fast on enemies facing him. After 2s, the light detonates, doing damage, applying another Slow stack, and increasing the Slow duration. Any enemies facing Ra at the time of the explosion are also Blinded. Additionally, Ra cleanses himself of slows and becomes immune to Slows for 0.6s when activated.', 'Ra summons a pillar of blessed light that persists for 6s. Allies inside the blessing have increased Protections and Power and are Healed every second. Enemies are damaged every second.', 'Ra calls on the power of the sun to decimate his foes in an extreme blast of heat in front of him, doing damage to all enemies unlucky enough to find themselves in the path.', 'Every time Ra uses an ability, his movement speed is increased.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/divine-light.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/solar-blessing.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/searing-pain.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/speed-of-light.jpg', '10 seconds', '12 seconds', '18 seconds', '80/75/70/65/60 seconds', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '65/75/85/95/105 mana', '90 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"