(85, 'Ratatoskr', 'The Sly Messenger', 'Norse', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/ratatoskr.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/ratatoskr.jpg', 'Dart', 'Flurry', 'Acorn Blast', 'Through the Cosmos', 'Acorn of Yggdrasil', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/dart.jpg', 'Ratatoskr dashes forward, damaging and slowing enemies for 3s. Dart pierces through minions and stops at the first god hit.\n\nAlso, Dart\'s cooldown is reduced by 1s for each enemy god hit by Flurry or Acorn Blast.', 'Ratatoskr spins around in a flurry of attacks, damaging nearby enemies and reducing their Physical Protections up to 4 times. ', 'Ratatoskr shoots a blast of three acorns forward in a cone, each dealing damage. Enemies hit by multiple acorns take 25% less damage on each acorn, down to a minimum of 25% damage. Enemies hit by 3 acorns are stunned. ', 'Ratatoskr charges up then leaps from the ground to a branch above his head. He may jump to 2 more branches before choosing a landing location. Upon landing he deals damage and Knocks up enemies. Through the Cosmos can be canceled or timed out from any of the branches, causing Ratatoskr to strike down at the current target location.', 'Ratatoskr spawns with a powerful Magic Acorn from the World Tree in his inventory, replacing his item slot for boots. He can upgrade this acorn through the item store from anywhere on the map. Each Acorn provides different bonuses to Ratatoskr.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/flurry.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/acorn-blast.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/through-the-cosmos.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/acorn-of-yggdrasil.jpg', '14 seconds', '14 seconds', '15 seconds', '110/105/100/95/90 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70  mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\