(86, 'Ravana', 'Demon King of Lanka', 'Hindu', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/ravana.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/ravana.jpg', 'Prana Onslaught', 'Overhead kick', '10-Hand Shadow Fist', 'Mystic Rush', 'Chain of Blows', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/prana-onslaught.jpg', 'Ravana throws a powerful punch, projecting his prana with it to damage and slow all enemies in front of him.', 'Ravana performs a high kick, sending a shockwave forward to damage all enemies in a line, increasing his Movement Speed and rendering him CC and damage immune for the duration.', 'Ravana\'s fists fly forward, damaging and passing through minions and damaging and rooting the first god hit. Ravana heals for each enemy hit - with maximum damage sources of one god and up to three minions.', 'Ravana leaps to a target location, damaging all enemies in the area and applying a debuff to enemy gods that increases the damage they take from all sources. After landing, Ravana receives a buff that reduces the damage he takes from all sources.', 'Successful Basic Attacks and abilities against an Enemy add to Ravana\'s Combo Chain.  Each time his Chain reaches 8 he receives a Shield equal to 5% of his Maximum Health as well as 3% Movement Speed. This may stack up to 3 times.\r\n', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/overhead-kick.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/10-hand-shadow-fist.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mystic-rush.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/chain-of-blows.jpg', '9 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '16 seconds', '110/105/100/95/90 seconds', '30/38/45/53/60 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\