(87, 'Scylla', 'Horror of the Sea', 'Greek', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/scylla.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/scylla.jpg', 'Sic \'Em', 'Crush', 'Sentinel', 'I\'m a Monster', 'Quick Learner', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sic-em.jpg', 'Scylla sends two hounds forward, damaging, Rooting, and Crippling the first enemy hit.\n\nAt max rank, two additional enemies nearby the first target will also be hit.', 'Scylla creates a Magical field that Slows enemies. After 5s it detonates and causes damage. Scylla may activate the ability again to detonate it early.\n\nAt max rank, enemies in the area also have their Magical Protection reduced, and targets hit by the damage are Slowed for 1s.', 'Passive: Scylla gains MP5.\n\nActive: Scylla summons a sentinel to the target area, granting vision of enemies for 5s. Scylla may activate the ability again within 5s to move to the sentinel location.\n\nAt max rank, the vision is granted through line of sight blockers, and placement range increases.', 'Scylla reveals her true nature, becoming immune to Crowd Control for the next 6s, and gaining movement speed. She may make one powerful attack during this time. If she kills an enemy god with the attack, she gains another 6s and may attack again.\n\nAt max rank, the movement speed bonus doubles.', 'Each of Scylla\'s abilities gain an additional effect at max rank. In addition, Scylla gains 25 Magical Power for each max rank ability.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/crush.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sentinel.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/im-a-monster.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/quick-learner.jpg', '10 seconds ', '10 seconds', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/70/80/90/100 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ward, Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/110/160/210/260 (+80% of your magical power)\"},{\"description\":\"Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.15/1.3/1.45/1.6/1.75s \"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/155/210/265/320 (0% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Max Rank Debuff:\",\"value\":\"isrank5/25% Magical Protection Reduced\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Passive MP5:\",\"value\":\"4/6/8/10/12\"},{\"description\":\"Vision Range:\",\"value\":\"40/50/60/70/80\"},{\"description\":\"Summon Range:\",\"value\":\"65/65/65/65/70\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Hit:\",\"value\":\"400/500/600/700/800 (120% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"35/35/35/35/70%\"}]', '[]'),
(88, 'Serqet', 'Goddess of Venom', 'Egyptian', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/serqet.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/serqet.jpg', 'Deathbane', 'Cobra\'s Kiss', 'Ambush', 'Last Breath', 'Catalyst', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/deathbane.jpg', 'Serqet dashes three times from side to side, dealing damage and applying Deathbane Poison to each enemy hit. This ability can Critical Hit, and Serqet is immune to Knockup while dashing.\n\nDeathbane Poison reduces a target\'s Physical Protection for a short time, and remains in a lingering dormant state for 20s.', 'Serqet launches her two blades forward, dealing damage and applying the Cobra\'s Kiss Poison.\n\nCobra\'s Kiss Poison drives gods to madness, forcing them to attack nearby allies dealing this damage again, or walk harmlessly towards Serqet. Cobra\'s Kiss remains in a lingering dormant state for 20s.', 'Serqet vanishes, Rooting herself in place. She may leap once, revealing herself and dealing damage to enemies. She will stay hidden until she leaps or cancels this ability. Enemy gods within range 12.5 will also reveal her.', 'Serqet leaps to an enemy, Stunning them, applying the Last Breath poison, then pushing them 30 units away. The Last Breath poison deals true damage to the target over the next 5s, and prevents them from healing. If an enemy dies while infected with Last Breath, they will explode, applying the poison to all enemies within 20 units.', 'Serqet\'s Basic Attacks apply Catalyst, which consumes her lingering poisons from Deathbane and Cobra\'s Kiss. If the target is affected by two or three different poisons, they take additional damage.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/cobras-kiss.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/ambush.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/last-breath.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/catalyst.jpg', '13 seconds', '16 seconds', '18 seconds', '90 seconds', '60 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '70 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Max Distance:\",\"value\":\"50\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"40\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"15\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Leap\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"True\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"10\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Passive\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/70/90/110/130 (+45% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Protection Reduction:\",\"value\":\"10% for 3s.\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/75/100/125/150 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Madness Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.0/1.1/1.2/1.3/1.4s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"80/140/200/260/320 (+70% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"140/230/320/410/500 (+55% of your Physical Power as True Damage)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun Duration:\",\"value\":\"1s\"},{\"description\":\"Healing Reduction:\",\"value\":\"All Healing\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"2 Poisons:\",\"value\":\"10% of target\'s maximum Health as Physical Damage.\"},{\"description\":\"3 Poisons:\",\"value\":\"20% of target\'s maximum Health as Physical Damage.\"}]'),
(89, 'Set', 'The Usurper', 'Egyptian', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/set.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/set.jpg', 'Skewer', 'Spawn of Set', 'Sandstorm', 'Kingslayer', 'Relentless', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/skewer.jpg', 'Set amasses his hatred, throwing it forward. Enemies caught in its path are damaged and slowed for 3s.\n\nSet\'s spawn are commanded when Set fires this attack, dashing towards a location Set determines. Enemies hit by a Spawn\'s dash take damage and are slowed for 3s. Any dash after the first will deal 40% damage. ', 'Set conjures a Spawn of himself made of sand. These spawn will stand where summoned and attack nearby enemies. Set can have up to 2 charges of this ability, allowing him to conjure spawn in quick succession. Set can interact with these Spawn with his other abilities, commanding them to attack or teleporting to them. Set can only have 8 Spawn at any given time.', 'Set conjures a Sandstorm around him, protecting him from Physical Damage and causing him to be immune to Slows. Enemies near Set are damaged every .4s for 6s and have their vision obscured by the sands.\n\nIf Set is targeting a spawn when this ability is cast he will immediately teleport to the spawn. Otherwise, he can reactivate this ability to teleport. Set can only teleport once per Sandstorm.', 'Set enrages, channeling his rage towards his enemies, gaining increased Movement Speed. Each time Set\'s attacks damage a god they gain a Mark of Set. At 4 Marks the target erupts. Enemies take a burst of damage on each explosion while Set becomes empowered, restoring Health and immediately gaining a charge of Spawn of Set. Excess charges are immediately consumed, causing a Spawn to appear near Set.', 'Each time Set damages an enemy, Set gains a stack of Relentless. If Horus is the enemy being damaged, Set gains 2 stacks. Each stack increases Set\'s Attack Speed. Relentless stacks to a max count of 10 for 6s. While Kingslayer is active, Relentless has no maximum stack count.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/spawn-of-set.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sandstorm.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/kingslayer.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/relentless.jpg', '8 seconds', '13/13/12/12/11 seconds', '16 seconds', '90 seconds', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '30 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '80/85/90/95/100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"60\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"70\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Teleport\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"16\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Stim\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"85/135/185/235/285 (+90% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Dash Range:\",\"value\":\"60 ft\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Attack Damage:\",\"value\":\"20 (+25% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Attack Range:\",\"value\":\"12 ft\"},{\"description\":\"Dash Damage:\",\"value\":\"60/65/70/75/80% of Skewer\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"8/9/10/11/12s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"8/12/16/20/24 (+7% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Physical Damage Reduction:\",\"value\":\"15%\"},{\"description\":\"Teleport Range:\",\"value\":\"65 ft\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"25/35/45/55/65 (30% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Heal:\",\"value\":\"45/55/65/75/85 (+25% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed:\",\"value\":\"25%\"},{\"description\":\"Duration:\",\"value\":\"12s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Attack Speed:\",\"value\":\"2.5%\"}]'),
(90, 'Skadi', 'Goddess of Winter', 'Norse', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/skadi.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/skadi.jpg', 'Piercing Cold', 'Rune of the Hunt', 'Permafrost', 'Winter\'s Grasp', 'Kaldr, The Winter Wolf', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/piercing-cold.jpg', 'Skadi throws an icy spear forward, dealing damage to enemies and Slowing them for 3s. Kaldr\'s basic attacks deal double damage to targets afflicted by Piercing Cold. ', 'Toggle: Skadi marks an enemy for Kaldr to hunt. While toggled on, Kaldr assumes Beast form, chasing and attacking the marked enemy. If a marked enemy dies Kaldr attacks other enemies nearby. When toggled off, Kaldr stops attacking and returns to Skadi, reverting to his Elemental form on the way. This ability can be activated at rank 0 and Kaldr gains new skills as it ranks up. ', 'Skadi freezes the ground for 5s at a target location. The icy area deals damage to enemies that touch it and continues to deal additional damage every .5s they stay on it. Gods who step on the ice are slowed and lose control of their movement while sliding across. Also, Skadi\'s movement speed increases while standing on the area and persists for 3s after it fades or she leaves.', 'A snowstorm surrounds Skadi as she chooses a location for Kaldr to attack. If Kaldr is too far he will leap there.\n\nUpon reaching the location a snowstorm also surrounds Kaldr. The initial hit of either snowstorm Roots enemies in the area and Kaldr is restored to full health. The storms persist for 4s while dealing damage to enemies every .5s.', 'Kaldr has 2 forms: Beast and Elemental. While in Beast form he can attack enemies and be attacked. While Elemental he is immune to attacks and gains 1 HP every 5s. He can be controlled with Rune of the Hunt but will revert into Elemental form if he loses all HP. Skadi also gains 10% Physical Power when Kaldr has no HP.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abiliti