(91, 'Sobek', 'God of the Nile', 'Egyptian', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/sobek.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/sobek.jpg', 'Charge Prey', 'Tail Whip', 'Sickening Strike', 'Lurking in the Waters', 'Blessing of the Nile', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/charge-prey.jpg', 'Sobek charges forward at a frenzied pace. If Sobek hits an enemy, he does damage and throws the enemy behind himself. Sobek is immune to Knockups whilst dashing.', 'Sobek whips around in a circle, knocking enemies back and doing damage.', 'Sobek does an axe attack that damages all enemies in front of him and lowers their healing received.  In addition, Sobek heals for each enemy hit, up to 3.', 'Sobek submerges himself, where he gains 20% protections, regenerates Mana, is immune to Crowd Control and he Slows all enemies. When Sobek emerges, he damages all enemies in the radius. Cancelling the ability decreases the damage.', 'Sobek\'s Basic Attacks and abilities that hit an enemy grant him Protections for a short time.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/tail-whip.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sickening-strike.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/lurking-in-the-waters.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/blessing-of-the-nile.jpg', '13 seconds', '14 seconds', '13 seconds', '90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\"