(92, 'Sol', 'Goddess of the Sun', 'Norse', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/sol.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/sol.jpg', 'Radiance', 'Stellar Burst', 'Disapparate', 'Supernova', 'Unstable Manifestation', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/radiance.jpg', 'Sol burns bright, gaining a large amount of Heat, Healing herself over time, and igniting the ground around her. Enemies that walk onto the fire take damage over time. The damaging area persists for 3s.', 'Sol\'s next basic attack explodes, creating a shockwave that travels out, dealing damage. At full size, the wave retracts, dealing damage again and slowing enemies.', 'Sol burns down her manifestation, gaining movement speed and immunity to Slows while leaving a trail of fire behind her that damages enemies.\r\n\r\nAfter 3s Sol loses corporeal form for a short time. Sol may leave her incorporeal form early.', 'Sol unleashes all her flame and fury from the sky, striking 8 times along a moveable ground target location. Enemies hit are knocked back on the first strike, and take only 30% damage on successive hits.', 'Sol gains Heat as she uses abilities and hits with basic attacks. She gains +1% Magical Power and +1% Attack Speed for every 4% Heat. At 100% Heat, Sol\'s basic attacks gain +20% Damage. Heat decreases over time.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/stellar-burst.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/disapparate.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/supernova.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/unstable-manifestation.jpg', '13 seconds', '10 seconds', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '60/70/80/90/100 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '60 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies and Self\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Stim\"},{\"description\":\"Affec