(93, 'SunWukong', 'the Monkey King', 'Chinese', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/sun-wukong.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/sun-wukong.jpg', 'The Magic Cudgel', 'Master\'s Will', '72 Transformations', 'Somersault Cloud', 'Undefeated Body', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/the-magic-cudgel.jpg', 'Sun Wukong\'s Magic Cudgel grows in length, and he slams it down, damaging all enemies in front of him. Minions and Jungle Camps take an extra +30% damage.', 'Sun Wukong strikes around him, damaging and Slowing all enemies.', 'Sun Wukong transforms into an Eagle, Tiger, or Ox, and charges forward.\n\nEagle: Is the fastest of the three forms. Immune to Slow and Root effects.\n\nTiger: Mauls the first enemy runs into, Stunning and causing damage.\n\nOx: Knocks aside all enemies in his path and causes damage. Immune to Slow, Root, and Knockup effects.', 'Sun Wukong leaps onto his cloud for up to 5s, leaving a Pet behind to fight. While on the cloud Sun Wukong is invisible, and regenerates Health. He may leap off before the duration expires, dealing damage. The Pet inherits 100% of Sun Wukong\'s Health and Protections and 50% of his Basic Attack Power. The Pet is killed instantly if hit by a hard Crowd Control excluding Banishes and Knockbacks. If the Pet dies, Sun Wukong is revealed on his cloud.', 'When Sun Wukong is below 50% Health, he gains +10 Physical Power and +10 Protections, plus another 2 Physical Power and 1 Protection for his current level. While Undefeated Body is active, if Sun Wukong goes above 50% Health, he maintains the buff for 12s.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/masters-will.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/72-transformations.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/somersault-cloud.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/undefeated-body.jpg', '12 seconds', '10 seconds', '18/17/16/15/14 seconds', '110/105/100/95/90 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 