(96, 'Terra', 'The Earth Mother', 'Roman', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/terra.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/terra.jpg', 'Force of Nature', 'Crushing Earth', 'Monolith', 'Earthen Fury', 'Standing Stones', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/force-of-nature.jpg', 'Terra gains momentum, causing her to charge forward and deal damage to enemies she passes through.\n\nTerra may charge through her own Standing Stones to Shatter them. If she does she may charge one more time within the next 3s.', 'Terra raises up two Standing Stone walls on either side of a target location. As long as both stones stand, Terra may activate this ability again to slam the stones together, damaging and Stunning enemies in between for 1.5s.\n\nThese stones can be Shattered into a cone of shrapnel with Force of Nature, damaging enemies in the area. ', 'Terra summons a Standing Stone monolith surging with natural energy. The monolith heals nearby allied gods every .5s for the duration but can be destroyed early if hit by 3 enemy basic attacks.\n\nTerra can Shatter this stone with Force of Nature to Root enemies in the area for 1s and create a damaging area that lasts 5s. ', 'Terra channels her strength into the world around her, buffing her allies and debuffing enemies for 10s.\nAllies gain 5% damage mitigation and protective stones that heal the ally if all 4 are activated as well as a Heal over Time.\nEnemies receive 5% more damage from all sources and harmful stones that damage the enemy if all 4 are activated.\nStones are activated when an ally or enemy receives damage.', 'Terra\'s abilities create Standing Stones. As long as any Standing Stones are on the battleground Terra becomes Knockup immune and her Basic Attacks will Slow enemies, deal bonus Basic Damage and cleave enemies in melee range. This Bonus Damage does not trigger item effects. If Terra Shatters any stones she will retain this buff for an additional 3s after