(99, 'Thor', 'God of Thunder', 'Norse', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/thor.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/thor.jpg', 'Mjolnir\'s Attunement', 'Tectonic Rift', 'Berserker Barrage', 'Anvil of Dawn', 'Warrior\'s Madness', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/mjolnirs-attunement.jpg', 'Thor throws Mjolnir forward, doing damage to all enemies in its path. If hit twice, minions will take 80% damage while gods take 200% damage from the return. While the hammer is flying, pressing the button again will teleport Thor to his hammer.', 'Thor slams his hammer on the ground, causing a fissure to appear in front of him, Stunning enemies and blocking movement.', 'Thor spins his hammer around him dealing damage to Enemies in front of him up to 3 times and those behind him up to 2 times. The final swing deals extra damage. Thor is immune to Knockup for the duration.', 'After a short buildup, Thor leaps into the air. While in the air, Thor can target a great distance away to come crashing down in the area, dealing damage and Stunning all enemies in the radius. For 6 seconds after landing, when Thor deals damage to a god with Mjolnir lightning will arc, damaging the enemy hit and up to two additional enemies within 30 ft. Subsequent lighting hits deal 50% damage.', 'Thor gains Physical Power for each enemy god within 30 units of him.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/tectonic-rift.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/berserker-barrage.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/anvil-of-dawn.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/warriors-madness.jpg', '12 seconds', '17/16.5/16/15.5/15 seconds', '10 seconds', '110/105/100/95/90 seconds', '70/75/80/85/90  mana', '60  mana', '55/60/65/70/75  mana', '80/90/100/110/120  mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile, Teleport\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Area\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"20\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"50/90/130/170/210 (+30% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1/1.15/1.3/1.45/1.6s\"},{\"description\":\"Fissure Lifetime:\",\"value\":\"3.7s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Tick:\",\"value\":\"30/50/70/90/110 (+35% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Final swing Damage:\",\"value\":\"45/65/85/105/125 (+50% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"100/150/200/250/300 (90% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Stun:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Arc Damage:\",\"value\":\"15/25/35/45/55 (+15% of your Physical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Physical Power:\",\"value\":\"10\"},{\"description\":\"Max Stacks:\",\"value\":\"3\"}]'),
(100, 'Thoth', 'Arbiter of the Damned', 'Egyptian', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/thoth.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/thoth.jpg', 'Hieroglyphic Assault', 'Evade and Punish', 'Glyph of Pain', 'Final Judgement', 'Dead Reckoning', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/hieroglyphic-assault.jpg', 'Thoth conjures three Hieroglyphs around him, ignoring the Basic Attack Movement penalty. His next 3 Basic Attacks pass through Enemies and apply Ability Damage instead. If these attacks pass through the Glyph of Pain, their range is increased by 30. Hitting an Enemy God with this ability increases the damage they take from each subsequent shot by 20% and reduces the cooldown by 1s (this can only occur once per shot).', 'Thoth dashes in the direction he is currently traveling. After dashing, for 5s Thoth\'s next basic attack is enhanced.\n\nThis projectile roots the first Enemy god hit while slowing all other Enemies, and also deals Ability Damage.\n\nIf either the Dash or Attack passes through the Glyph of Pain, their respective range is increased by 30.', 'From his book, Thoth conjures forth a Hieroglyph in front of him. Thoth\'s ability projectiles passing through the glyph receive increased damage, and a range increase of 30. This damage does not trigger Item effects.\r\n\n\nThoth and allies\' Basic Attack projectiles also receive a lesser damage bonus, but no range increase.', 'Thoth conjures a large glyph from his book, and then inscribes three more at its corners. When all four have been summoned, he sends them forward damaging all Enemies in their path.\n\nThoth may activate this ability again to fire the ability early, doing a reduced amount of damage based on the number of glyphs currently summoned. Alternately he may cancel this ability at a cost of 30 mana.', 'Thoth pens the names of his fallen opponents in his book, recording their weaknesses. After killing 30 Enemies, Thoth gains a stack of 3 Magical Penetration, and killing an Enemy God will complete the current stack. He unlocks a new stack every 4 levels, up to a maximum of 5 stacks at level 17.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/evade-and-punish.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/glyph-of-pain.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/final-judgement.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/dead-reckoning.jpg', '8 seconds', '16/15/14/13/12 seconds', '5 seconds', '90 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '25/30/35/40/45 mana', '100 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff and Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Thoth and Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash Special\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Thoth and Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self and Allies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"55\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"100\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Level 1:\",\"value\":\"Max 1 Stack\"},{\"description\":\"Level 5:\",\"value\":\"Max 2 Stacks\"},{\"description\":\"Level 9:\",\"value\":\"Max 3 Stacks\"},{\"description\":\"Level 13:\",\"value\":\"Max 4 Stacks\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage per Shot:\",\"value\":\"45/65/85/105/125 (+20% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Glyphs Spawned:\",\"value\":\"3\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"70/110/150/190/230 (+60% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Root Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"},{\"description\":\"Slow:\",\"value\":\"30%\"},{\"description\":\"Slow Duration:\",\"value\":\"1.5s\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability Bonus Damage:\",\"value\":\"15/25/35/45/55 (+5% of your Magical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Basic Attack Damage:\",\"value\":\"10/15/20/25/30 (+5% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"360/430/500/570/640 (120% of your Magical Power)\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Kills for One Stack:\",\"value\":\"30\"},{\"description\":\"Penetration:\",\"value\":\"3 per Stack\"},{\"description\":\"Max Penetration:\",\"value\":\"15 at 5 Stacks\"}]'),
(101, 'Tsukuyomi', 'God of the Moon', 'Japanese', 'Melee, Physical', 'Assassin', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/tsukuyomi.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/tsukuyomi.jpg', 'Dark Moon Shuriken', 'Kusarigama', 'Silver Moon Caltrops', 'Piercing Moonlight', 'Shingetsu & Mangetsu', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/dark-moon-shuriken.jpg', 'Tsukuyomi calls upon Shingetsu, summoning forth a Dark Moon Shuriken. The Shuriken damages enemies and stops on gods, sticking into them. If Tsukuyomi gets close to the god he retrieves the Shuriken and reduces its cooldown.\n\n<font color=\'#b18cd9\'>After casting this ability Shingetsu\'s next Basic Attack becomes ranged. This attack steals Movement Speed from the enemy hit.</font>', 'Shingetsu and Mangetsu form themselves into a Kusarigama. Tsukuyomi swings the weapon to his left and right, damaging and disarming enemies hit. He then swings the weapon forward with more force stunning enemies hit. While channeling Tsukuyomi gains 25% Movement Speed.', 'Tsukuyomi holds Mangetsu aloft as it erupts into starlight, sending stars falling to the ground. As they land they become Caltrops, damaging enemies in the area and slowing them for 1.5s. Enemies who move inside this Caltrop field take damage and are slowed again. \n\n<font color=\'#DFEAFA\'>After casting this ability Mangetsu\'s next Basic Attack becomes ranged. This attack deals bonus Physical Damage.</font>', 'Tsukuyomi channels the power of the Full Moon, gaining Crowd Control immunity and 30% Damage Reduction. He fires forward 4 powerful piercing beams of moonlight. Enemy gods damaged become marked. Each beam can hit up to 3 enemy gods. After firing all beams Tsukuyomi charges forward at light speed, dashing through all enemies in the order they were hit, dealing heavy damage. Tsukuyomi will end his dashing at the final enemy hit.\n\nIf Tsukuyomi kills an enemy god with this ability Tsukuyomi he will gain both of his ranged basic attacks.', 'Tsukuyomi wields Shingetsu in his left hand and Mangetsu in his right hand. When these weapons damage an enemy they become empowered. <font color=\'#b18cd9\'>Empowered Shingetsu gains a 50% cleave and restores mana.</font> <font color=\'#DFEAFA\'>Empowered Mangetsu deals bonus damage and restores health.</font>', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/kusarigama.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/silver-moon-caltrops.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/piercing-moonlight.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/shingetsu-&-mangetsu.jpg', '10 seconds', '14 seconds', '14 seconds', '90 seconds', '50/60/70/80/90 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"65\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Circle & Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"25\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Crescent\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"35\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"90\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Type:\",\"value\":\"Stim\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Shuriken Damage:\",\"value\":\"85/135/185/235/285 (+80% of your Physical Power)\"},{\"description\":\"Cooldown Reduction:\",\"value\":\"4s\"},{\"description\":\"Movement Speed Steal:\",\"value\":\"25%\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Swing Damage:\",\