(102, 'Tyr', 'the Lawgiver', 'Norse', 'Melee, Physical', 'Warrior', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/tyr.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/tyr.jpg', 'Fearless', 'Power Cleave', 'Change Stance', 'Lawbringer', 'Unyielding', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/fearless.jpg', 'Tyr charges forward, immune to Knockup, damaging enemies.\r\nAssault Stance: Tyr pushes all enemies along with him, hitting them 2 times and knocking them up in the air.\r\nGuard Stance: Tyr hits each enemy only once, passing through and knocking them up in the air.', 'Tyr makes a massive melee attack, hitting all enemies within a 180 degree cone.\n\nAssault Stance: Enemies that are knocked up in the air are knocked away.\n\nGuard Stance: Tyr heals himself for each enemy hit (max 3).', 'Tyr changes between Assault and Guard stances. Changing stances refreshes the cooldown on Fearless and Power Cleave.\n\nAssault Stance: Gain Physical Power.\n\nGuard Stance: Gain Protections.', 'Tyr leaps through the air, bringing indiscriminate justice upon all enemies in the target area, and Slowing them.', ' Stuns, Taunts, Fears, Intoxicate, and Mesmerize cannot affect Tyr for longer than 1s.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/power-cleave.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/change-stance.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/lawbringer.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/unyielding.jpg', '15 seconds', '12/11/10/9/8 seconds', '12/12/11/11/10 seconds', '90/85/80/75/70 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '50 mana', ' mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Radius:\",\"value\":\"12\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"},{\"description\":\"Cone:\",\"v