(103, 'Ullr', 'The Glorious One', 'Norse', 'Ranged, Physical', 'Hunter', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/ullr.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/ullr.jpg', 'Bladed Arrow (Thrown Axe)', 'Expose Weakness (Invigorate)', 'Hail of Arrows (Glory Bound)', 'Wield Axes (Wield Bow)', 'Weapon Master', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/bladed-arrow.jpg', 'Ranged: Ullr fires a bladed arrow in a line, dealing damage and passing through all targets it hits.\n\nMelee: Ullr throws an axe in a line, hitting a single target dealing damage and Stunning it.', 'Ranged: Ullr gains bonus Physical Power for 5s.\n\nMelee: Ullr gains bonus move speed for 5s.', 'Ranged: Ullr fires a volley at his target location, dealing damage.\n\nMelee: Ullr leaps to his target location, dealing damage in an AoE on arrival.', 'Ullr changes stance.\n\nRanged: Ullr uses his yew bow, removing Disarms and gaining additional attack speed.\n\nMelee: Ullr uses his axes, removing Disarms and gaining additional Physical Lifesteal.', 'When Ullr uses an ability in either stance his Cooldowns in the opposite stance are reduced.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/expose-weakness.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/hail-of-arrows.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/wield-axes.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/weapon-master.jpg', '14 seconds', '16 seconds', '15 seconds', '1 seconds', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '50 mana', '60/65/70/75/80 mana', '0 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Self\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Ground Target\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Physical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Buff\"},{\"descrip