(105, 'Vulcan', 'Smith of the Gods', 'Roman', 'Ranged, Magical', 'Mage', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/vulcan.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/vulcan.jpg', 'Backfire', 'Inferno Cannon', 'Magma Bomb', 'Earthshaker', 'Master Craftsman', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/backfire.jpg', 'Vulcan blasts a fireball out of his Forge, pushing him back and dealing damage to all enemies in its path, marking the first god that is hit.  The Inferno Cannon prioritizes the marked target and deals 15% more damage to that god.', 'Vulcan constructs an Inferno Cannon that shoots fireballs in a cone that deal damage to the target every second. The Inferno Cannon lasts until destroyed or another is placed. This inherits Vulcan\'s penetrations but does not apply on-hit effects. Inferno Cannon takes 50% additional damage from non-god sources. Inferno Cannon ignores 25% of the target\'s Magical Protection.', 'Vulcan tosses a bomb that explodes in a radius on impact with the ground, damaging and knocking back nearby enemies.', 'Vulcan launches a rocket that explodes on impact with the ground. The rocket starts at 75% strength, and increases damage the further it travels from Vulcan.', 'Whenever Vulcan successfully hits an enemy god with an ability he gains bonuses to Movement Speed and MP5 for 5s.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/inferno-cannon.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/magma-bomb.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/earthshaker.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/master-craftsman.jpg', '7/6.5/6/5.5/5 seconds', '15 seconds', '10 seconds', '90 seconds', '40/45/50/55/60 mana', '65/70/75/80/85 mana', '50/55/60/65/70 mana', '80/90/100/110/120 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Projectile, Dash\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemy\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Pet\"},{\"description\":\"Affects: