(107, 'XingTian', 'The Relentless', 'Chinese', 'Melee, Magical', 'Guardian', NULL, 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-icons/xing-tian.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-cards/xing-tian.jpg', 'Furious Roar', 'Hook Slam', 'Sky-Cutting Axe', 'Whirlwind of Rage and Steel', 'Smouldering Rage', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/furious-roar.jpg', 'Xing Tian shouts from his chest with great force, damaging enemies and reducing their Basic Attack damage.  Enemies also take damage over time based on their maximum health.', 'Xing Tian first launches an attack with his axe, knocking the opponents into the air before slamming them into the ground and rooting them.', 'Xing Tian leaps forward, dealing damage to enemies when he lands, and he may leap again within 3s. While in the air, Xing Tian has increased protections, which are refreshed if he connects with a target.', 'Xing Tian spins grabbing and hitting enemies with his axe before throwing them in the direction he is facing.\n\nDamage is dealt to enemies once each on the grab and throw as well as three times during the spin.', 'Xing Tian gains stacks of Smouldering Rage each time he hits an enemy with an ability. For each stack of rage Xing Tian has, he gains HP5.\n\nStacks last 18s.', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/hook-slam.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sky-cutting-axe.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/whirlwind-of-rage-and-steel.jpg', 'https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/smouldering-rage.jpg', '14 seconds', '18 seconds', '15 seconds', '90 seconds', '55/60/65/70/75 mana', '70/75/80/85/90 mana', '65/75/85/95/105 mana', '110/100/90/80/70 mana', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Line\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{\"description\":\"Damage:\",\"value\":\"Magical\"},{\"description\":\"Range:\",\"value\":\"45\"}]', '[{\"description\":\"Ability:\",\"value\":\"Cone, AOE\"},{\"description\":\"Affects:\",\"value\":\"Enemies\"},{